#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "<color_yellow>Project: Packrat</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>囤囤鼠计划</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_yellow>Project: Packrat</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Endgame high-tech mod. More information is available in README.md."
msgstr "终局高科技模组。更多信息请参阅 README.md。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "ranger lightweight combat armor"
msgid_plural "ranger lightweight combat armors"
msgstr[0] "游骑兵轻型战斗装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ranger lightweight combat armor'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized non-powered lightweight combat armor with excellent defense and "
"mobility, great for dangerous missions. With a distinctive look and feel, "
"this is the dignity of non-powered combat armor for survivors."
msgstr "定制无动力轻型战斗装甲，具有卓越的防御力和机动性，非常适合危险任务。独特的外观和手感，这是幸存者无动力战斗装甲的尊严。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Power Actuator"
msgstr "动力促动器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Power Actuator'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Powerful hydraulic pistons mounted on your combat armor bring your punching "
"power to practical levels. Greatly increases the damage of unarmed attacks."
msgstr "安装在战斗装甲上的强力液压活塞，将你的拳击力量提升到实用水平。大幅增加徒手攻击伤害。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Warden' heavy combat armor"
msgid_plural "'Warden' heavy combat armors"
msgstr[0] "“典狱长”重型战斗装甲"



#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Warden' heavy combat armor"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"A customized powered heavy combat suit. It's design was inspired by adapting "
"and scaling down version of DoubleTech's Power Armor in a survivor's style. "
"While it has limited protection compared to real power armor, this rugged, "
"clunky look ensures that the armor will work. When used, it activates the "
"arm's powerful motor."
msgstr "一件定制动力重型战斗服。其设计灵感源于将DoubleTech动力装甲以幸存者风格改编并缩小。虽然与真正的动力装甲相比防护有限，但这种粗犷笨重的外观确保装甲能正常工作。使用时激活手臂的强力电机。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Warden' heavy combat armor (on)"
msgid_plural "'Warden' heavy combat armors (on)"
msgstr[0] "“典狱长”重型战斗装甲（开启）"



#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Warden' heavy combat armor (on)", 'str_pl':
#. "'Warden' heavy combat armors (on)"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"A customized powered heavy combat suit. It's design was inspired by adapting "
"and scaling down version of DoubleTech's Power Armor in a survivor's style. "
"While it has limited protection compared to real power armor, this rugged, "
"clunky look ensures that the armor will work. Use to stop it from "
"functioning."
msgstr "一件定制动力重型战斗服。其设计灵感源于将DoubleTech动力装甲以幸存者风格改编并缩小。虽然与真正的动力装甲相比防护有限，但这种粗犷笨重的外观确保装甲能正常工作。使用以停止运行。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Circulatory System Manager"
msgstr "循环系统管理器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Circulatory System Manager'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"The combat armor monitors your circulatory and respiratory systems, and "
"absorbs oxygen directly into your skin through artificial muscle fibers. "
"Your maximum stamina is increased, and your stamina regeneration rate "
"increases dramatically."
msgstr "战斗装甲监控你的循环和呼吸系统，通过人造肌肉纤维直接将氧气吸收到你的皮肤中。你的最大耐力得到提升，耐力恢复速度大幅增加。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Rampart' assault armor"
msgid_plural "'Rampart' assault armors"
msgstr[0] "“壁垒”突击装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Rampart' assault armor"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized semi-rigid power armor that is internally powered by UPS. "
"Basically built like a human-shaped tank with superalloy plates and layered "
"carbides all over its body, it augments the wearer's strength and protects "
"against most physical threats. When used, it augments defense."
msgstr "定制半刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。基本上像人形坦克一样建造，全身覆盖超合金板和层压碳化物，增强穿戴者的力量并抵御大多数物理威胁。使用时增强防御。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Rampart' assault armor (on)"
msgid_plural "'Rampart' assault armors (on)"
msgstr[0] "“壁垒”突击装甲（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Rampart' assault armor (on)", 'str_pl':
#. "'Rampart' assault armors (on)"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized semi-rigid power armor that is internally powered by UPS. "
"Basically built like a human-shaped tank with superalloy plates and layered "
"carbides all over its body, it augments the wearer's strength and protects "
"against most physical threats. It is turned on, and continually draining "
"power.  Use it to turn it off."
msgstr "定制半刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。基本上像人形坦克一样建造，全身覆盖超合金板和层压碳化物，增强穿戴者的力量并抵御大多数物理威胁。已开启，持续消耗电力。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Pioneer' environmental carapace"
msgid_plural "'Pioneer' environmental carapaces"
msgstr[0] "“先驱者”环境甲壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Pioneer' environmental carapace"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized non-rigid power armor that is internally powered by UPS. Built to "
"survive in the worst environments, including cryogenic and hyperthermal "
"regions. It protects you from all kinds of hazards, including psychic "
"attacks and teleportation sickness. It provides X-ray vision for "
"exploration, allowing you to see through terrain. When used, it completely "
"ignores the effects of temperature and allows for a wider range of vision."
msgstr "定制非刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。为在最恶劣环境中生存而建，包括低温和超高温区域。保护你免受各种危害，包括精神攻击和传送病。提供X光视野用于探索，让你能看穿地形。使用时完全忽略温度影响并可获得更广视野。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Transmissive Scanner System"
msgstr "透射扫描系统"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Transmissive Scanner System'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"The combat armor's scanners and high-performance processor analyze and image "
"the surrounding terrain and show it to you. Your night vision range "
"dramatically increases and you can see through walls."
msgstr "战斗装甲的扫描仪和高性能处理器分析并成像周围地形并展示给你。你的夜视范围大幅增加，可以看穿墙壁。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Pioneer' environmental carapace (on)"
msgid_plural "'Pioneer' environmental carapaces (on)"
msgstr[0] "“先驱者”环境甲壳（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Pioneer' environmental carapace (on)",
#. 'str_pl': "'Pioneer' environmental carapaces (on)"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized non-rigid power armor that is internally powered by UPS. Built to "
"survive in the worst environments, including cryogenic and hyperthermal "
"regions. It protects you from all kinds of hazards, including psychic "
"attacks and teleportation sickness. It provides X-ray vision for "
"exploration, allowing you to see through terrain. It is turned on, and "
"continually draining power.  Use it to turn it off."
msgstr "定制非刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。为在最恶劣环境中生存而建，包括低温和超高温区域。保护你免受各种危害，包括精神攻击和传送病。提供X光视野用于探索，让你能看穿地形。已开启，持续消耗电力。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Synaptic Augmented Reflexes"
msgstr "突触增强反射"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Synaptic Augmented Reflexes'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"The controls of your combat armor tap into your neural network to boost your "
"motor and reflexes. Dodging becomes easier, and you can now move as if you "
"were on flat ground on ledges, stalls, etc. that are blocking you."
msgstr "战斗装甲的控制系统接入你的神经网络，提升你的运动和反射能力。闪避变得更容易，你现在可以在阻挡你的窗台、货摊等障碍物上如履平地般移动。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Corsair' blitz strike suit"
msgid_plural "'Corsair' blitz strike suits"
msgstr[0] "“海盗”闪击战服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Corsair' blitz strike suit"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized non-rigid power armor that is internally powered by UPS. Built "
"for rapid infiltration and exfiltration, it is equipped with aiming aids and "
"synaptic accelerators to drastically improve the wearer's perception and "
"reaction speed.When used, it grants the wearer an extremely high speed of "
"action for 10 turns, as if time had stopped."
msgstr "定制非刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。为快速渗透和撤离而建，配备瞄准辅助和突触加速器，大幅提升穿戴者的感知和反应速度。使用时赋予穿戴者10回合极高行动速度，仿佛时间停止。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "survivor combat armor"
msgid_plural "survivor combat armors"
msgstr[0] "幸存者战斗装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor combat armor'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built armor made from a bulletproof vest and a jumpsuit with "
"circuitry inserted into it, designed to internally powered by UPS. Based on "
"the design of the Rivtech RM13 Combat Armor. Some features have been omitted "
"due to difficulty of interpreting technology and for productivity, but it "
"still protects you from the elements as well as from harm. It is turned on, "
"and continually draining power.  Use it to turn it on."
msgstr "一件由防弹背心和植入电路的连体服制成的定制装甲，设计由UPS内部供能。基于Rivtech RM13战斗装甲的设计。由于技术解读困难和生产力原因省略了一些功能，但仍能保护你免受自然元素的伤害和物理损伤。已开启，持续消耗电力。使用以开启。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "survivor combat armor (on)"
msgid_plural "survivor combat armors (on)"
msgstr[0] "幸存者战斗装甲（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor combat armor (on)', 'str_pl': 'survivor
#. combat armors (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built armor made from a bulletproof vest and a jumpsuit with "
"circuitry inserted into it, designed to internally powered by UPS. Based on "
"the design of the Rivtech RM13 Combat Armor. Some features have been omitted "
"due to difficulty of interpreting technology and for productivity, but it "
"still protects you from the elements as well as from harm. It is turned on, "
"and continually draining power.  Use it to turn it off."
msgstr "一件由防弹背心和植入电路的连体服制成的定制装甲，设计由UPS内部供能。基于Rivtech RM13战斗装甲的设计。由于技术解读困难和生产力原因省略了一些功能，但仍能保护你免受自然元素的伤害和物理损伤。已开启，持续消耗电力。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "powered suit schematics"
msgid_plural "powered suit schematics"
msgstr[0] "动力战服图纸"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'powered suit schematics'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Assembly plans, design specs, and technical drawings for the powered suit.  "
"Most of this is useless to you, but you could use the assembly plans to re-"
"assemble the suit from salvaged parts."
msgstr "动力战服的装配计划、设计规格和技术图纸。大部分对你没用，但你可以使用装配计划从回收零件重新组装战服。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Integrated Combat System"
msgstr "集成战斗系统"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Integrated Combat System'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"The nano-foam structure of the combat armor's endothelium aids in the body's "
"recovery from damage. Your speed to recover from pain and perceptive "
"abilities will increase dramatically while wearing it."
msgstr "战斗装甲内皮层的纳米泡沫结构有助于身体从伤害中恢复。穿着时你从疼痛中恢复的速度和感知能力将大幅提升。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Legion' powered suit"
msgid_plural "'Legion' powered suits"
msgstr[0] "“军团”动力战服"


#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': "'Legion' powered suit"}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Integrated weapon storage container"
msgstr "集成武器储存容器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Legion' powered suit"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized military grade non-rigid power armor that is internally powered "
"by UPS. It's a trifecta of mobility, durability, and lethality. With a built-"
"in energy weapon generation system and six expansion weapon slots, the "
"ST-301 'Legion' is the combat armor for the next generation of super "
"soldiers. When used, it generates a plasma impact grenade in the form of a "
"combat knife."
msgstr "定制军用级非刚性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。机动性、耐久性和杀伤力的三重奏。配备内置能量武器生成系统和六个扩展武器槽，ST-301“军团”是下一代超级士兵的战斗装甲。使用时以战斗刀形式生成等离子冲击手雷。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "assassin suit schematics"
msgid_plural "assassin suit schematics"
msgstr[0] "暗杀服图纸"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'assassin suit schematics'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Assembly plans, design specs, and technical drawings for the assassin suit.  "
"Most of this is useless to you, but you could use the assembly plans to re-"
"assemble the suit from salvaged parts."
msgstr "暗杀服的装配计划、设计规格和技术图纸。大部分对你没用，但你可以使用装配计划从回收零件重新组装战服。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "Active Camouflage System"
msgstr "主动伪装系统"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Active Camouflage System'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"The combat armor is equipped with a fluid armor structure using liquefied "
"smart metal, a noise-canceling system, and a breathing filter. The wearer's "
"range of recognition is reduced by 40%, and footsteps and body odor are also "
"masked, providing complete stealth when using the Invisibility feature. "
"Additionally, the extra liquefied metal in the armor can form blades to "
"amplify unarmed damage."
msgstr "战斗装甲配备使用液化智能金属的流体装甲结构、降噪系统和呼吸过滤器。穿戴者的识别范围降低40%，脚步声和体味被掩盖，使用隐身功能时提供完全潜行。此外，装甲中额外的液化金属可形成刀刃以增强徒手伤害。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suit"
msgid_plural "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suits"
msgstr[0] "“亡魂”暗杀渗透服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suit"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized military grade flexible power armor that is internally powered by "
"UPS. Equipped with active optical cloaking using refraction of a liquid "
"smart metal that bonds with the user, Latitude Industries' R34-P 'Revenant' "
"Assassination Infiltration Suit was used in small numbers to assassinate "
"enemy nationals in the event of a nuclear war between the United States and "
"China. It cancels footsteps and body odor when worn, and turns on stealth "
"mode when used."
msgstr "定制军用级柔性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。配备使用与使用者结合的液态智能金属折射的主动光学隐形，纬度工业R34-P“亡魂”暗杀渗透服曾在中美核战争情景下少量用于暗杀敌方要员。穿着时消除脚步声和体味，使用时开启潜行模式。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suit (on)"
msgid_plural "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suits (on)"
msgstr[0] "“亡魂”暗杀渗透服（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suit
#. (on)", 'str_pl': "'Revenant' assassination infiltration suits (on)"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor.json
msgid ""
"Customized military grade flexible power armor that is internally powered by "
"UPS. Equipped with active optical cloaking using refraction of a liquid "
"smart metal that bonds with the user, Latitude Industries' R34-P 'Revenant' "
"Assassination Infiltration Suit was used in small numbers to assassinate "
"enemy nationals in the event of a nuclear war between the United States and "
"China. It is turned on, and continually draining power.  Use it to turn it "
"off."
msgstr "定制军用级柔性动力装甲，由UPS内部供能。配备使用与使用者结合的液态智能金属折射的主动光学隐形，纬度工业R34-P“亡魂”暗杀渗透服曾在中美核战争情景下少量用于暗杀敌方要员。已开启，持续消耗电力。使用以关闭。"

