#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "earth shockwave"
msgstr "地裂震波"

#. ~ Description for earth shockwave
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid ""
"Slam the ground with the armor's power, knocking down nearby enemies and "
"dealing bash damage."
msgstr "用护甲的力量猛击地面，击倒附近敌人并造成钝击伤害。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "wall breaker"
msgstr "碎墙击"

#. ~ Description for wall breaker
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Breaks walls within one tile around you."
msgstr "破坏你周围一格内的墙壁。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Acceleration"
msgstr "加速"


#. ~ Message for SPELL 'Acceleration'
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Time feels like it's moving slower."
msgstr "时间感觉变慢了。"



#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "TX-01 plasma grenade launcher"
msgstr "TX-01等离子榴弹发射器"



#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "target acquired"
msgstr "已锁定目标"

#. ~ Description of effect 'target acquired'.
#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'target acquired'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "You have been acquired by a tactical scope!"
msgstr "你已被战术瞄准镜锁定！"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Phantom tactical scope"
msgstr "幻影战术瞄准镜"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Plasma Impact Grenade"
msgstr "等离子冲击榴弹"

#. ~ Description for Plasma Impact Grenade
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plasma impact knife'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid ""
"The unstable plasma material is wrapped in a hardlight sheath, shaped into a "
"throwable knife. Due to the nature of hardlights, they do not retain their "
"shape for long without a constant power supply, but the knife tip is still "
"razor sharp. If it receives a strong impact, such as being thrown and hit "
"the ground, it will explode in a powerful blast with a pillar of flame."
msgstr "不稳定的等离子材料包裹在硬光护套中，塑造成可投掷的刀。由于硬光的特性，没有持续供电时无法长时间保持形状，但刀尖依然锋利无比。如果受到强烈冲击（如被投掷后撞击地面），它将爆炸成一股强大的烈焰柱。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "plasma impact knife"
msgid_plural "plasma impact knifes"
msgstr[0] "等离子冲击刀"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Frost Reflection"
msgstr "冰霜反射"

#. ~ Description for Frost Reflection
#: .\items\advtech\sq_advanced_armor_spells.json
msgid "Reflects frostbite onto the attacker."
msgstr "将冻伤反射给攻击者。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frozen shard"
msgid_plural "frozen shards"
msgstr[0] "冰冻碎片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frozen shard', 'str_pl': 'frozen shards'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A jagged shard of unmelting ice pulsating with necrotic energy. It is "
"unsettlingly cold to the touch, whispering of the endless winter from whence "
"it came. A crucial component for crafting gear that defies the warmth of "
"life."
msgstr "一片锯齿状不融之冰，充满坏死能量。触感令人不安地冰冷，低语着它所来自的无尽寒冬。是打造违逆生命温暖装备的关键部件。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frozen core"
msgid_plural "frozen cores"
msgstr[0] "冰冻核心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frozen core', 'str_pl': 'frozen cores'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A crystalline heart torn from the chest of an apex winter aberration. It "
"contains the raw, concentrated essence of the abyssal cold. Holding it feels "
"like clutching a piece of the fading world's inevitable end."
msgstr "从一头顶级寒冬异怪胸膛中撕下的结晶心脏。内含原始浓缩的深渊之寒。握住它就像抓住世界凋零不可避免终结的碎片。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frost-covered map fragment"
msgid_plural "frost-covered map fragments"
msgstr[0] "覆霜地图碎片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost-covered map fragment', 'str_pl': 'frost-
#. covered map fragments'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A torn, severely frostbitten piece of paper recovered from the corpse of a "
"frozen undead. The ink is smeared, but it clearly details topographical "
"coordinates. You will need a few more of these to figure out exactly where "
"they lead."
msgstr "一张从冰冻亡灵尸体上回收的撕裂、严重冻伤的纸片。墨水模糊不清，但清晰标出了地形坐标。你还需要几张才能确定它们究竟指向何处。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "map to the frozen cave"
msgid_plural "map to the frozen caves"
msgstr[0] "通往冰冻洞穴的地图"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'map to the frozen cave'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Several frost-covered fragments meticulously taped together. The complete "
"topographical data points to an isolated region of absolute zero. Activating "
"the map will peel back the veil of reality, forcing a passage into the "
"frozen abyss where the dragon waits. If this map is destroyed, the pocket "
"dimension connected to it will also collapses."
msgstr "几张覆霜碎片被仔细粘贴在一起。完整的地形数据指向一个绝对零度的孤立区域。激活地图将揭开现实的面纱，强行打开通往巨龙等待的冰冻深渊的通道。如果这张地图被摧毁，与之相连的口袋维度也将崩塌。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "blood-stained surveyor's note"
msgid_plural "blood-stained surveyor's notes"
msgstr[0] "血染的勘测笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "blood-stained surveyor's note"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A hastily scribbled note found on a frozen corpse. It reads:\n"
"\n"
"'Turn back. The undead dragon slumbers at the abyss of this frozen hell. The "
"narrow, pitch-black cavern makes long-range combat impossible. If you try to "
"keep your distance, its frostfire breath will obliterate you. Do NOT hug the "
"walls—the breath shatters against the rock, and the ice shrapnel will tear "
"you to shreds. If you step too close, its blizzard will freeze you solid. "
"Your only hope? Wait for the brief lull after it unleashes its cold, pack "
"the thickest thermal armor you can find, and smash its skull in melee. Do "
"not cower. Hesitation means death.'"
msgstr "一张在冻僵尸体上匆忙写就的纸条。上面写着：\\\\n\\\\n回去吧。不死龙沉睡着，在这冰冻地狱的深渊中。狭窄漆黑的洞穴让远程战斗毫无可能。如果你想保持距离，它的霜火吐息会将你化为灰烬。不要贴着墙壁——吐息会在岩石上碎裂，冰片弹片会把你撕碎。如果你靠得太近，它的暴风雪会将你冻结凝固。你唯一的机会？等到它释放寒冷之后的短暂停顿，穿上最厚实的隔热装甲，在近战中砸碎它的头颅。不要退缩。犹豫意味着死亡。"





#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frozen dragon heart"
msgid_plural "frozen dragon hearts"
msgstr[0] "永冻龙心脏"

#. ~ Description for frozen dragon heart
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"The literal heart of the permafrost dragon, still pulsating with abyssal "
"cold and raw, untamed power. Consuming its essence will infuse your body "
"with the power of the winter sovereign. If you dismantle it, you can obtain "
"additional frozen shards and frozen cores."
msgstr "永冻龙的真正心脏，仍在脉动着深渊寒冷和原始、未驯服的力量。吞噬其精华将使你的身体注入寒冬君主的力量。如果拆解它，可以获得额外的冰冻碎片和冰冻核心。"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "Frozen Heart"
msgstr "冰冻之心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Frozen Heart'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"The abyssal cold of the dragon's heart has frozen your own. Stripped of all "
"distracting emotions, guilt, and hesitation, your mind is now a realm of "
"absolute clarity. Free from the weaknesses of a normal human, you can focus "
"entirely on unlocking your raw, untapped potential, elevating all of your "
"physical and mental attributes."
msgstr "龙心的深渊之寒已冻结了你自己的心。剥离了所有分散注意力的情感、内疚和犹豫，你的心智如今是绝对清晰的领域。摆脱了普通人的弱点，你可以完全专注于解锁你原始未开发的潜能，提升你所有身体和精神属性。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "journal of the winter blacksmith"
msgid_plural "journal of the winter blacksmiths"
msgstr[0] "冬日铁匠日志"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'journal of the winter blacksmith'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A weathered journal bound in an unknown, freezing leather. It details the "
"obsessive research of a blacksmith who discovered how to bind 'frozen core' "
"into steel without the metal shattering. It contains esoteric methods to "
"perfectly fuse the absolute zero energy of a frozen core into conventional "
"cold weapons, granting them an unmelting, lethal edge."
msgstr "一本以未知冰冷皮革装订的破旧日志。详述了一位铁匠的痴迷研究，他发现了如何将"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "synthesis notes: cryo-light weaponry"
msgid_plural "synthesis notes: cryo-light weaponrys"
msgstr[0] "合成笔记：冰光武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'synthesis notes: cryo-light weaponry'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A personalized binder containing a brilliant synthesis of Mizuno's hardlight "
"theories and the winter blacksmith's cryogenic metallurgy. It outlines the "
"ultimate blueprints for channeling a complete frozen core into localized "
"force fields, giving birth to devastating high-tech cryo weapons."
msgstr "一本个性化活页夹，内含水野硬光理论与冬日铁匠低温冶金的绝妙综合。概述了将完整冰冻核心引导为局部力场的终极蓝图，催生出毁灭性的高科技冰霜武器。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "permafrost dagger"
msgid_plural "permafrost daggers"
msgstr[0] "永冻匕首"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost dagger'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A lethal dagger forged by embedding a frozen core fragment into the steel. "
"Its blade constantly emits a chilling mist, freezing the blood of its "
"victims before they even realize they've been cut."
msgstr "将冰冻核心碎片嵌入钢中锻造的致命匕首。刀刃持续散发寒雾，在受害者还未意识到被割伤前就已冻结其血液。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "permafrost sword"
msgid_plural "permafrost swords"
msgstr[0] "永冻剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost sword'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A medieval-style arming sword infused with a frozen core fragment. The blade "
"is unnaturally cold and never dulls, leaving a trail of frost with every "
"swing."
msgstr "注入冰冻核心碎片的中世纪风格武装剑。刀刃异常寒冷且永不钝化，每次挥斩都留下霜痕。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "permafrost spear"
msgid_plural "permafrost spears"
msgstr[0] "永冻矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost spear'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A stout polearm tipped with a spearhead carved from a frozen core fragment. "
"It pierces armor with ease, instantly flash-freezing the internal organs of "
"its target."
msgstr "一根坚固的长杆武器，矛头以冰冻核心碎片雕刻而成。轻松穿透护甲，瞬间闪冻目标的内脏。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "permafrost battle axe"
msgid_plural "permafrost battle axes"
msgstr[0] "永冻战斧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost battle axe'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A massive battle axe with a heavy head forged from steel and a frozen core "
"fragment. It shatters bones and freezes the marrow in a single, devastating "
"sweep."
msgstr "以钢铁和冰冻核心碎片锻造重型斧头的巨大战斧。一次毁灭性的横扫便粉碎骨骼并冻结骨髓。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "permafrost greatsword"
msgid_plural "permafrost greatswords"
msgstr[0] "永冻巨剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost greatsword'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"An enormous two-handed sword infused with the raw power of a frozen core. To "
"wield it is to swing a glacier; it leaves nothing but shattered, frozen "
"corpses in its wake."
msgstr "注入冰冻核心原始力量的巨剑。挥动它如同挥动冰川；身后只留下粉碎、冻结的尸体。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-blade dagger (off)"
msgid_plural "cryo-blade daggers (off)"
msgstr[0] "冰刃匕首（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-blade dagger (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-
#. blade daggers (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "You activate the dagger. A terrifyingly cold energy blade hums to life."
msgstr "你启动了匕首。一道可怖的冷光能量刀刃嗡鸣苏醒。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-blade dagger (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-blade
#. daggers (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A high-tech hilt housing a frozen core as its power source. When activated, "
"it projects a condensed blade of absolute zero energy. It is currently off."
msgstr "高科技剑柄，内含冰冻核心作为能源。激活时投射出浓缩的绝对零度能量刀刃。当前关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-blade dagger (on)"
msgid_plural "cryo-blade daggers (on)"
msgstr[0] "冰刃匕首（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-blade dagger (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-
#. blade daggers (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "You deactivate the cryo-blade."
msgstr "你关闭了冰刃。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-blade dagger (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-blade
#. daggers (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A high-tech hilt projecting a condensed blade of absolute zero energy. The "
"air around it crackles with frost. It is currently on."
msgstr "投射浓缩绝对零度能量刀刃的高科技剑柄。周围空气因霜冻噼啪作响。当前开启。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-edge sword (off)"
msgid_plural "cryo-edge swords (off)"
msgstr[0] "冰锋剑（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-edge sword (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-edge
#. swords (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"The cryo-edge ignites with a blinding cyan flash, dropping the room's "
"temperature."
msgstr "冰锋以耀眼的青色闪光点燃，降低了室内温度。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-edge sword (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-edge
#. swords (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A sophisticated sword hilt powered by a frozen core. It is designed to emit "
"a searingly cold energy blade capable of slicing through molecular bonds. It "
"is currently off."
msgstr "由冰冻核心供能的精密剑柄。设计用于发射一道灼冷的能量刀刃，能切割分子键。当前关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-edge sword (on)"
msgid_plural "cryo-edge swords (on)"
msgstr[0] "冰锋剑（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-edge sword (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-edge
#. swords (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "You shut down the cryo-edge."
msgstr "你关闭了冰锋。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-edge sword (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-edge
#. swords (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A sophisticated sword hilt projecting a searingly cold energy blade. It "
"leaves a trail of falling snow with every movement. It is currently on."
msgstr "投射灼冷能量刀刃的精密剑柄。每个动作都留下飘落的雪花轨迹。当前开启。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-lance (off)"
msgid_plural "cryo-lances (off)"
msgstr[0] "冰霜骑枪（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-lance (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-lances
#. (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "The cryo-lance extends with a harsh crackle of freezing air."
msgstr "冰霜骑枪以刺耳的冻气噼啪声展开。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-lance (off)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-lances
#. (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced polearm chassis wired to a frozen core. It is capable of "
"projecting a massive, freezing lance of energy. It is currently off."
msgstr "连接冰冻核心的强化长杆武器底架。能投射出巨大的冰冻能量骑枪。当前关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "cryo-lance (on)"
msgid_plural "cryo-lances (on)"
msgstr[0] "冰霜骑枪（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'cryo-lance (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-lances
#. (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "You deactivate the cryo-lance."
msgstr "你关闭了冰霜骑枪。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cryo-lance (on)', 'str_pl': 'cryo-lances (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced polearm chassis projecting a massive, freezing lance of "
"absolute zero energy. The very air around the tip condenses into ice. It is "
"currently on."
msgstr "投射巨大绝对零度冰冻能量骑枪的强化长杆武器底架。枪尖周围的空气直接凝结成冰。当前开启。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "avalanche greatsword (off)"
msgid_plural "avalanche greatswords (off)"
msgstr[0] "雪崩巨剑（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'avalanche greatsword (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'avalanche greatswords (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"With a thunderous roar, the avalanche greatsword forms a massive pillar of "
"freezing energy!"
msgstr "伴随雷鸣般的咆哮，雪崩巨剑形成了一根巨大的冰冻能量柱！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'avalanche greatsword (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'avalanche greatswords (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"An oversized, highly advanced hilt built around a complete frozen core. When "
"powered, it generates an impossibly large blade of destructive cryogenic "
"energy. It is currently off."
msgstr "围绕完整冰冻核心构建的超大型高度先进剑柄。供能时生成一柄不可思议的毁灭性低温能量巨剑。当前关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "avalanche greatsword (on)"
msgid_plural "avalanche greatswords (on)"
msgstr[0] "雪崩巨剑（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'avalanche greatsword (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'avalanche greatswords (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "You power down the avalanche greatsword."
msgstr "你关闭了雪崩巨剑。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'avalanche greatsword (on)', 'str_pl': 'avalanche
#. greatswords (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"An impossibly large blade of destructive cryogenic energy protrudes from the "
"hilt. It illuminates the area with a terrifying, ghostly blue light. It is "
"currently on."
msgstr "一柄不可思议的毁灭性低温能量巨剑从剑柄中伸出。以可怖的幽灵蓝光照亮周围。当前开启。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm FCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A 9x19mm round tipped with a frozen core fragment. Upon firing, it trails a "
"chilling mist and injects absolute zero temperatures directly into the "
"target."
msgstr "9x19mm弹药，尖端嵌有冰冻核心碎片。发射时拖出一道寒雾，将绝对零度温度直接注入目标。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56x45mm FCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A 5.56x45mm round tipped with a frozen core fragment. It shatters armor "
"through rapid thermal contraction and freezes internal organs instantly."
msgstr "5.56x45mm弹药，尖端嵌有冰冻核心碎片。通过快速热收缩粉碎护甲，瞬间冻结内脏。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm FCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A high-caliber 7.62x51mm round embedded with a frozen core fragment. The "
"impact alone can flash-freeze a limb, trailing a deadly blizzard in its wake."
msgstr "高口径7.62x51mm弹药，嵌入冰冻核心碎片。仅冲击力就能闪冻肢体，尾迹拖着致命的暴风雪。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '.50 BMG FCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"An anti-material .50 BMG round housing a significant chunk of a frozen core. "
"It doesn't just pierce engine blocks; it reduces them to brittle, frozen "
"shards that shatter into dust."
msgstr "反器材.50 BMG弹药，内含一大块冰冻核心。它不仅仅穿透发动机缸体；它将它们还原成脆弱的冰冻碎片，化为粉尘。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frost arrow"
msgid_plural "frost arrows"
msgstr[0] "冰霜箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost arrow', 'str_pl': 'frost arrows'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Arrow crafted by fusing a frozen core into its shaft. It freezes targets "
"upon impact, delivering absolute zero temperature directly into their flesh."
msgstr "将冰冻核心融入箭杆中制作的箭矢。命中时冻结目标，将绝对零度温度直接送入其肉体。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "frost bolt"
msgid_plural "frost bolts"
msgstr[0] "冰霜矢"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost bolt', 'str_pl': 'frost bolts'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Bolt crafted by fusing a frozen core into its shaft. It freezes targets upon "
"impact, delivering absolute zero temperature directly into their flesh."
msgstr "将冰冻核心融入矢杆中制作的弩矢。命中时冻结目标，将绝对零度温度直接送入其肉体。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "stabilized portal freezer"
msgid_plural "stabilized portal freezers"
msgstr[0] "稳定传送门冰柜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stabilized portal freezer'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Peering into the frostbitten maw of this localized dimensional tear, an old-"
"world truth chills you to the bone. There are only two things that are truly "
"bottomless: the freezing void of the universe, and a survivor's kleptomania."
msgstr "凝视这个局部维度撕裂的冻伤之口，一句旧世界的真理让你寒彻骨髓。只有两样东西是真正无尽的：宇宙的冰冻虚空，以及幸存者的盗窃癖。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "abyssal frost ring"
msgid_plural "abyssal frost rings"
msgstr[0] "深渊冰霜戒指"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'abyssal frost ring'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A ring carved entirely from frozen fragments. It emits a faint mist and "
"protects the wearer from the biting cold. (cold resistance +2)"
msgstr "完全由冰冻碎片雕刻而成的戒指。散发微弱雾气，保护佩戴者免受刺骨寒冷。（寒冷抗性+2）"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "abyssal frost tiara"
msgid_plural "abyssal frost tiaras"
msgstr[0] "深渊冰霜头冠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'abyssal frost tiara'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A delicate yet terrifying tiara woven from frozen fragments. It chills the "
"brow but acts as a powerful ward against lethal frost. (cold resistance +5)"
msgstr "以冰冻碎片编织的精致而可怖的头冠。使额头寒冷但作为抵御致命冰霜的强大护符。（寒冷抗性+5）"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "abyssal frost cufflinks"
msgid_plural "abyssal frost cufflinks"
msgstr[0] "深渊冰霜袖扣"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'abyssal frost cufflinks'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Cufflinks made of sheer ice from the abyss. They radiate a protective chill "
"over the wearer's arms. (cold resistance +3)"
msgstr "由深渊纯冰制成的袖扣。向佩戴者手臂散发防护寒霜。（寒冷抗性+3）"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "pair of abyssal frost earrings"
msgid_plural "pairs of abyssal frost earrings"
msgstr[0] "深渊冰霜耳环（一对）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of abyssal frost earrings', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of abyssal frost earrings'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Earrings crafted from frozen fragments. The cold they emit acts as a shield "
"against the harsh winter. (cold resistance +2)"
msgstr "以冰冻碎片制作的耳环。散发寒冷作为抵御严冬的护盾。（寒冷抗性+2）"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "abyssal frost pendant necklace"
msgid_plural "abyssal frost pendant necklaces"
msgstr[0] "深渊冰霜吊坠项链"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'abyssal frost pendant necklace'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A necklace bearing frozen fragments. Resting close to the heart, it offers "
"significant protection against extreme cold. (cold resistance +3)"
msgstr "承载冰冻碎片的项链。贴近心脏，提供对极端寒冷的显著防护。（寒冷抗性+3）"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "Abyssal Chill"
msgstr "深渊寒意"

#. ~ Description for Abyssal Chill
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"The unmelting frost from your abyssal gear seeps into your very flesh, "
"acting as a relentless heat sink. It constantly saps your body heat, leaving "
"you unnaturally cold."
msgstr "来自深渊装备的不融霜冻渗入你的肉体，充当无情的散热器。持续吸取你的体温，让你异常寒冷。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "glacial plate armor"
msgid_plural "glacial plate armors"
msgstr[0] "冰川板甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glacial plate armor'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A massive suit of heavy armor forged by pouring molten frost cores between "
"steel plates. Unmelting frost clings to its surface. Worn by heretic knights "
"who rejected the flame, it inflicts bone-chilling agony upon the wearer."
msgstr "将熔融霜冻核心浇铸在钢板间铸造的巨大重型护甲。不融霜冻附着其表面。由拒绝火焰的异端骑士穿戴，给穿戴者带来刺骨痛苦。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "mantle of the fading fire"
msgid_plural "mantle of the fading fires"
msgstr[0] "消逝之火斗篷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mantle of the fading fire'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Woven from the hides of beasts claimed by the abyssal cold and infused with "
"ground frost core fragments. It scatters a faint blue blizzard even in pitch-"
"black darkness. It reflects frostbite onto attackers but constantly saps "
"your own body heat."
msgstr "以被深渊寒冷夺取的野兽皮编织，注入研磨的冰冻核心碎片。即使在漆黑中也能散发微弱的蓝色暴风雪。将冻伤反射给攻击者但持续吸取你自身的体温。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "rimebound hunter's garb"
msgid_plural "rimebound hunter's garbs"
msgstr[0] "霜缚猎衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "rimebound hunter's garb"}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"Assassin's garb woven from the pelts of winter horrors and infused with the "
"biting chill of a frozen core. The unmelting frost clinging to the fabric "
"naturally distorts the wearer's silhouette, granting exceptional camouflage. "
"It allows you to blend seamlessly into both the frozen wastes and ruined "
"cities as a silent predator."
msgstr "以冬日恐怖生物的毛皮编织并注入冰冻核心刺骨寒冷的暗杀者服装。附着在布料上的不融霜冻自然扭曲穿戴者轮廓，提供卓越伪装。让你无声无息地融入冰冻废土和废墟城市，成为沉默的掠食者。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid "crown of the abyssal monarch"
msgid_plural "crown of the abyssal monarchs"
msgstr[0] "深渊君主之冠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crown of the abyssal monarch'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_frost_tier.json
msgid ""
"A grotesque helm with a complete frozen core embedded dead center. The "
"moment it is worn, human fear and frailty freeze over, leaving only the cold "
"logic of annihilation. However, it leaves the mind dangerously exposed to "
"nether whispers."
msgstr "一顶可怖的头盔，正中嵌有一颗完整冰冻核心。戴上瞬间，人类的恐惧和脆弱被冻结，只留下冰冷的湮灭逻辑。然而，它使心智危险地暴露于虚空低语。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "tesla cannon"
msgid_plural "tesla cannons"
msgstr[0] "特斯拉炮"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The tesla cannon is a survivor's masterpiece that uses electromagnetic waves "
"to disable enemy equipment and turn the battlefield into chaos. The emitted "
"electromagnetic wave is transferred to other enemies within 4 tiles."
msgstr "特斯拉炮是幸存者的杰作，利用电磁波瘫痪敌方设备并使战场陷入混乱。发射的电磁波会传递到4格内的其他敌人。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
#: .\items\item_common\sq_weapon_override.json .\monsters\sq_mech_weapons.json
#: .\monsters\sq_walkers.json
msgid "semi"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "photon solidification matrix"
msgid_plural "photon solidification matrixs"
msgstr[0] "光子固化矩阵"

#. ~ Description for photon solidification matrix
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Photonic solid-state technology, which captures and stores photons, has a "
"wide range of applications by treating photons as particles. This small "
"projector provides the ability to capture and store photons as they interact "
"with common materials."
msgstr "光子固态技术，通过将光子视为粒子来捕获和存储，具有广泛应用。这个小型投影仪提供捕获和存储光子与常见材料相互作用的能力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "fusion core"
msgid_plural "fusion cores"
msgstr[0] "聚变核心"

#. ~ Description for fusion core
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The mechanical heart that powers the smallest stars. A power reactor that "
"reliably supplies energy from the nuclear fusion of hydrogen accelerated by "
"the force of uranium. Optical inertial confinement and a time delay using "
"portal technology succeed in stabilizing the energy release."
msgstr "驱动最微小星辰的机械心脏。一个通过铀力加速氢核聚变可靠供应能量的动力反应堆。利用光学惯性约束和传送门技术的时间延迟成功稳定了能量释放。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "lab journal-Mizuno"
msgid_plural "lab journals-Mizuno"
msgstr[0] "实验室日志—Mizuno"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lab journal-Mizuno', 'str_pl': 'lab journals-
#. Mizuno'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This lab report covers the various applications of the technique of "
"disturbing the wave of a photon and treating it like a solid. At the end of "
"one formula, which you barely recognized as part of a wave function, was a "
"solution with units of time that you had never seen before.'' ''So we need "
"to make a circuit that flashes the switch on and off at these intervals.'' "
"''Dr. Mizuno. If the circuit flashes for such a short period of time, it's "
"bound to be affected by its own electromagnetic field.'' ''It's your job "
"from there. You didn't do your PhD for nothing, did you?''"
msgstr "此实验室报告涵盖扰动光子波并将其视为固体的各种技术应用。在一条你勉强认出的波函数公式末尾，出现了一个你从未见过时间单位的解。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "lab journal-Red"
msgid_plural "lab journals-Red"
msgstr[0] "实验室日志—Red"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lab journal-Red', 'str_pl': 'lab journals-Red'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This joint report presents blueprints for a military weapon that utilizes a "
"reactor the size of the palm of your hand. At first glance, the word uranium "
"is described in a highly paranoid manner. [Disapproved]: this fusion power "
"plant is remarkable for its size, but because it ultimately uses the fission "
"of uranium, it cannot escape the threat of radioactive waste."
msgstr "此联合报告展示了利用手掌大小反应堆的军用武器蓝图。乍一看，铀这个词以极为偏执的方式描述。[否决]：这个聚变发电厂的尺寸令人瞩目，但因为它最终使用铀的裂变，无法摆脱放射性废料的威胁。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight multi-tool"
msgid_plural "hardlight multi-tools"
msgstr[0] "硬光多功能工具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hardlight multi-tool', 'str_pl': 'hardlight
#. multi-tools'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This is the ultimate field multi-tool that converts energy into physical "
"form using a built-in light-solidification matrix. When you flip the switch, "
"light particles solidify into the shapes of all the tools you need, such as "
"wrenches, saw blades, and welders. No need to lug around a bulky toolbox—"
"this single compact device handles most construction and repair tasks."
msgstr "这是终极野外多功能工具，利用内置光固化矩阵将能量转化为物理形态。拨动开关时，光粒子固化成你需要的所有工具形状，如扳手、锯片和焊机。无需拖着笨重的工具箱——这一个小巧的设备就能处理大多数建造和维修任务。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56x45mm HVP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A 5.56x45mm high velocity round with a depleted uranium penetrator that "
"unleashed the full potential of the rifle round. It had improved damage and "
"penetration over the original 5.56mm."
msgstr "5.56x45mm高速弹药，配备贫铀侵彻体，释放步枪弹的全部潜能。比原始5.56mm弹药具有更高的伤害和穿透力。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm HVP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A 7.62x51mm high velocity round with a depleted uranium penetrator that "
"unleashed the full potential of the rifle round. It had greater destructive "
"power and penetration than the original 7.62mm."
msgstr "7.62x51mm高速弹药，配备贫铀侵彻体，释放步枪弹的全部潜能。比原始7.62mm弹药具有更高的破坏力和穿透力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "delpleted uranium rail"
msgid_plural "delpleted uranium rails"
msgstr[0] "贫铀轨弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'delpleted uranium rail'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A piece of steel cast with a depleted uranium core. Can be used as a "
"projectile for electromagnetic weapons."
msgstr "一块含贫铀芯的钢铸件。可用作电磁武器的弹丸。"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight sidearm"
msgid_plural "hardlight sidearms"
msgstr[0] "硬光副武器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Firing bolts of solidified photons, the energy sidearm is a precursor to "
"hardlight firearms technology. It has a somewhat shorter range than a normal "
"laser weapon, but it is highly penetrative and packs a lot of firepower."
msgstr "发射固化光子弹的能量副武器，是硬光枪械技术的前身。射程比普通激光武器稍短，但穿透力极强且火力充足。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight scatter gun"
msgid_plural "hardlight scatter guns"
msgstr[0] "硬光散射枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A hardlight energy shotgun designed for both overwhelming crowd control and "
"firepower at close range. Although it's a shotgun, it's actually more of a "
"specializer: photon shards with a sharp cross-section scatter and refract "
"towards nearby victims."
msgstr "专为压倒性群体控制和近距离火力设计的硬光能量霰弹枪。虽然名为霰弹枪，实则更像专家武器：具有锐利截面的光子碎片散射并折射向附近的受害者。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight carbine"
msgid_plural "hardlight carbines"
msgstr[0] "硬光卡宾枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A small energy carbine that fires a storm of solidified photon needles. With "
"better portability and faster aiming than the hardlight rifle, you'll be "
"able to surprise enemies around corners."
msgstr "一种发射固化光子针风暴的小型能量卡宾枪。比硬光步枪更便携且瞄准更快，让你能在转角处突袭敌人。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight rifle"
msgid_plural "hardlight rifles"
msgstr[0] "硬光步枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The Hardlight Energy Rifle is an energy weapon that uses a mechanism called "
"a 'photon solidification matrix'. It fires rapid-fire bolts of solidified "
"photons, and while it has a somewhat shorter range than a conventional "
"assault rifle, it is fast and extremely accurate, making it highly effective "
"in medium-range engagements."
msgstr "硬光能量步枪是一种使用“光子固化矩阵”机制的能量武器。它能速射固化光子弹，虽然射程比传统突击步枪稍短，但速度快且极为精准，在中距离交战中非常有效。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight precision rifle"
msgid_plural "hardlight precision rifles"
msgstr[0] "硬光精确步枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"An energy precision rifle that fires bolts of solidified, high-powered "
"photons. It has a shorter range and lower stopping power than other assault "
"rifles, making it harder to disrupt enemies from a distance, but its "
"improved aiming system and low noise make up for it, allowing for darting in "
"and out maneuvers."
msgstr "发射固化高能光子弹的能量精确步枪。射程和制止力不如其他突击步枪，更难在远处扰乱敌人，但其改进的瞄准系统和低噪音弥补了不足，适合快速穿插的机动战术。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight longbow"
msgid_plural "hardlight longbows"
msgstr[0] "硬光长弓"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A sleek, stringless, superalloy longbow that uses UPS power to run at high "
"efficiency. Each shot creates a string and arrow of powerful light instantly "
"through a projector. These systems provide exceptional accuracy and "
"penetration."
msgstr "一把流线型无弦超合金长弓，由UPS供能高效运行。每次射击通过投影仪瞬间生成强大的光之弓弦和箭矢。这些系统提供卓越的精度和穿透力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight glaive (off)"
msgid_plural "hardlight glaive (off)s"
msgstr[0] "硬光戟（关闭）"


#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'hardlight glaive (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "You turn on hardlight glaive."
msgstr "你开启了硬光戟。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hardlight glaive (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This weapon is a chimera of Eastern and Western culture, a sci-fi recreation "
"of an ancient Chinese weapon. Not to mention its cutting power, the hilt is "
"made of superalloy. You can be the warlord of legend, but it's up to you to "
"find the long beard and red horse."
msgstr "这件武器是东西方文化的嵌合体，古代中国武器的科幻再造。且不说其切割力，剑柄由超合金制成。你可以成为传说中的战神，但要找到长须和赤马就得靠你自己了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hardlight glaive (on)"
msgid_plural "hardlight glaives (on)"
msgstr[0] "硬光戟（开启）"


#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'hardlight glaive (on)', 'str_pl': 'hardlight
#. glaives (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "You turn off hardlight glaive."
msgstr "你关闭了硬光戟。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hardlight glaive (on)', 'str_pl': 'hardlight
#. glaives (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This weapon is a chimera of Eastern and Western culture, a sci-fi recreation "
"of an ancient Chinese weapon. Not to mention its cutting power, the hilt is "
"made of superalloy. You can be the warlord of legend, but it's up to you to "
"find the long beard and red horse.  Use to turn it off."
msgstr "这件武器是东西方文化的嵌合体，古代中国武器的科幻再造。且不说其切割力，剑柄由超合金制成。你可以成为传说中的战神，但要找到长须和赤马就得靠你自己了。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss revolver"
msgid_plural "Gauss revolvers"
msgstr[0] "高斯左轮手枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The deserted cities of the apocalypse are dangerous, so take this revolver "
"with you. Firing a superheated metal rail, your trusty five-shot atomic "
"Gauss revolver will put holes in the heads of heavily armed bandits like no "
"other, faster than anyone else."
msgstr "末日荒城危机四伏，带上这把左轮吧。发射过热的金属轨弹，你那可靠的五发原子高斯左轮将以无人能及的速度在全副武装的匪徒头上开洞。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "fan"
msgstr "扇面射击"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss cluster cannon"
msgid_plural "Gauss cluster cannons"
msgstr[0] "高斯集束炮"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Gauss flak gun powered by a small fusion core. Great for taking out densely "
"packed enemies, its supercooled metal rail rounds unleash a storm of "
"shrapnel on impact, devastating the surrounding area."
msgstr "由小型聚变核心供能的高斯高射炮。对付密集敌人非常出色，过冷金属轨弹命中时释放弹片风暴，席卷周围区域。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss rifle"
msgid_plural "Gauss rifles"
msgstr[0] "高斯步枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A gauss rifle powered by a small fusion core. It's heavy, bulky, and slow to "
"fire, but the firepower to electromagnetically blast through walls and cars "
"alike makes up for it. It's an electromagnetic projectile-firing weapon that "
"utilizes Fleming's left-hand rule, but we shoot it with the index finger of "
"our right hand; our left hand is just a girdle."
msgstr "由小型聚变核心供能的高斯步枪。沉重、笨重且射速缓慢，但能电磁轰穿墙壁和汽车的强大火力足以弥补。这是利用弗莱明左手定则的电磁弹丸发射武器，但我们用右手食指开火；左手只是摆设。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss driver"
msgid_plural "Gauss drivers"
msgstr[0] "高斯驱动器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"The Gauss anti-materiel sniper rifle is an oddly constructed weapon with an "
"enlarged double rail that takes up most of the barrel, forgoing ergonomics "
"for the sole purpose of sending pure firepower over long distances. There's "
"no better weapon for delivering the sunday punch to the most powerful enemy."
msgstr "高斯反器材狙击步枪，结构奇特，扩大的双轨占据大部分枪管，牺牲人体工学只为将纯粹火力送达远方。对付最强大敌人的致命一击，没有比它更好的武器了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss assault cannon"
msgid_plural "Gauss assault cannons"
msgstr[0] "高斯突击炮"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A very fleshy and beautiful Gaussian heavy arm. Equipped with a second "
"fusion core for extra firepower. Powered by two hearts, this great "
"conversationalist unleashes an endless stream of heated metal shards."
msgstr "一挺非常丰润优美的重型高斯武器。配备第二颗聚变核心以获取额外火力。由两颗心脏驱动，这位大演说家倾泻出无尽的炙热金属碎片。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "high auto"
msgstr "高速自动"




#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "hammer blow"
msgstr "锤击"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "heavy knockback attack, 166% bash and stab damage"
msgstr "重型击退攻击，166%打击和刺击伤害"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> strike %s down for the finishing blow."
msgstr "<npcname>给予%s致命一击。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "fusion rocket hammer"
msgid_plural "fusion rocket hammers"
msgstr[0] "聚变火箭锤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fusion rocket hammer'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A massive rocket-propelled siege hammer powered by a fusion core. In "
"addition to hammering, it can project super-hot flames from its nuclear core "
"to unleash a fiery inferno on distant enemies. With a crimson-accented body "
"and a depleted uranium coating, the hammer's head is a force of "
"indiscriminate destruction. Only the toughest of men can handle this weapon, "
"which is why it's called the Weapon of Kings. Be careful when you wield it. "
"Unless you wish to fuse your loved ones with the earth."
msgstr "由聚变核心驱动的巨型火箭推进攻城锤。除锤击外，还能从核芯投射超高温火焰对远处敌人释放火海。深红配色的锤体和贫铀涂层使锤头成为不分青红皂白的毁灭之力。只有最坚韧的人才能驾驭此武器，因此被称为王者之器。挥舞时请小心。除非你想把你所爱之人也与大地融合。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "compact rail speedloader"
msgid_plural "compact rail speedloaders"
msgstr[0] "紧凑型轨弹快速装弹器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'compact rail speedloader'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This is a speedloader for Gaussian weapons. It holds 8 rail rounds and "
"allows for quick loading of compatible firearms."
msgstr "用于高斯武器的快速装弹器。容纳8发轨弹，可快速装填兼容枪械。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "standard rail speedloader"
msgid_plural "standard rail speedloaders"
msgstr[0] "标准型轨弹快速装弹器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'standard rail speedloader'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This is a speedloader for Gaussian weapons. It holds 25 rail rounds and "
"allows for quick loading of compatible firearms."
msgstr "用于高斯武器的快速装弹器。容纳25发轨弹，可快速装填兼容枪械。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "large rail speedloader"
msgid_plural "large rail speedloaders"
msgstr[0] "大型轨弹快速装弹器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large rail speedloader'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This is a speedloader for Gaussian weapons. It holds 50 rail rounds and "
"allows for quick loading of compatible firearms."
msgstr "用于高斯武器的快速装弹器。容纳50发轨弹，可快速装填兼容枪械。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "smart pistol module"
msgid_plural "smart pistol modules"
msgstr[0] "智能手枪模块"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This pistol module is a labor of love for DoubleTech engineers. Featuring "
"smart auto-aim with motion sensors, the smart pistol module includes "
"technology to automatically aim the bullet at the target to aid in accurate "
"shooting. With technologies such as bullet tracking and auto-aim, this "
"module provides high accuracy for shooting at relatively short distances."
msgstr "这款手枪模块是DoubleTech工程师的心血结晶。配备带运动传感器的智能自动瞄准，智能手枪模块包含自动将子弹瞄准目标以辅助精确射击的技术。借助子弹追踪和自动瞄准等技术，该模块在相对短距离射击时提供高精度。"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "ballistic coprocessor"
msgid_plural "ballistic coprocessors"
msgstr[0] "弹道协处理器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This smartgun module is the pride of DoubleTech engineers and incorporates "
"smart features that provide improved accuracy and shooting efficiency. With "
"features such as bullet path calculation and environmental condition "
"monitoring, this module significantly improves the hit rate of shots and is "
"applied to military precision rifles."
msgstr "这款智能枪模块是DoubleTech工程师的骄傲，融合了智能功能以提供更高精度和射击效率。具备弹道路径计算和环境条件监测等功能，该模块显著提高命中率，应用于军用精确步枪。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "quick reloader"
msgid_plural "quick reloaders"
msgstr[0] "快速装弹器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A collection of attachments that efficiently load firearms, allowing you to "
"quickly load bullets or magazines to increase your survivability in combat."
msgstr "一套高效装载枪械的附件集合，让你能快速装填子弹或弹匣，提高战斗中的生存力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "electromagnetic projectile accelerator"
msgid_plural "electromagnetic projectile accelerators"
msgstr[0] "电磁弹丸加速器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Converts firearm into an electrothermal cannon. The firearm's damage output "
"is greatly increased, but it uses power from the UPS. This experimental "
"device generates and fires an effective amount of heat to destroy targets, "
"making it particularly good at long-range strikes and penetrating obstacles. "
"With enough electronics and mechanical knowledge, you might be able to build "
"something even more awesome."
msgstr "将枪械转换为电热炮。枪械输出伤害大幅提升，但消耗UPS电力。该实验装置产生并发射有效热量来摧毁目标，特别擅长远程打击和穿透障碍物。具备足够的电子和机械知识，你也许能造出更厉害的东西。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "overcharged railgun expansion mod"
msgid_plural "overcharged railgun expansion mods"
msgstr[0] "超载电磁炮扩展模块"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Warning!\n"
"This tool can damage your firearm!\n"
"Use at your own risk!\n"
"The Overcharged RailGun Expansion mod, or O.R.G.E for short, is a monstrous "
"overmodification of the electromagnetic projectile accelerator (EPA) module. "
"This overclocked firearm attachment transforms your weapon from a gun "
"chamber to a thermochemical cannon, dramatically increasing its damage "
"output, but also making it more power hungry and heavier."
msgstr "警告！\\\\n该工具可能损坏你的枪械！\\\\n使用风险自负！\\\\n超载电磁炮扩展模块，简称ORGE，是对电磁弹丸加速器(EPA)模块的怪兽级过度改装。这个超频枪械附件将你的武器从枪膛变为热化学炮，大幅提升伤害输出，但也使其更耗电更沉重。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "advanced noise suppressor"
msgid_plural "advanced noise suppressors"
msgstr[0] "高级消音器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Greatly reduces the noise and muzzle flame generated when firing. Internal "
"sound-absorbing material with applied nanoparticles effectively eliminates "
"noise."
msgstr "大幅减少射击时产生的噪音和枪口火焰。内部应用纳米颗粒的吸音材料有效消除噪音。"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "suppressor MK II"
msgid_plural "suppressor MK IIs"
msgstr[0] "消音器MK II"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A suppressor reduces the amount of noise and muzzle flash generated by the "
"report of a firearm. Gunfire is extremely loud and can damage your hearing "
"without protection; this improved military silencer greatly suppresses the "
"sound of gunfire and improves shooting accuracy."
msgstr "消音器减少枪械射击产生的噪音和枪口闪光。枪声极其响亮，无保护会损伤听力；这款改良军用消音器大幅抑制枪声并提高射击精度。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "rifling barrel"
msgid_plural "rifling barrels"
msgstr[0] "膛线枪管"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A gun barrel with an elongated spiral groove carved into the inside of the "
"barrel, which causes the bullet to rotate along the spiral groove as it "
"travels. The angular momentum from the rotation causes the bullet to follow "
"a stable trajectory that is less affected by ambient air currents and wind."
msgstr "在枪管内部刻有细长螺旋凹槽的枪管，使子弹在行进时沿螺旋槽旋转。旋转产生的角动量使子弹遵循更稳定的弹道，较少受环境气流和风的影响。"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "shotgun choke"
msgid_plural "shotgun chokes"
msgstr[0] "霰弹枪喉缩"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A firearm attachment that tightens the muzzle diameter of a shotgun by "
"squeezing inside the muzzle buttstock. How tightly you tighten the choke "
"determines the dispersion of the shot, which is important to hunters."
msgstr "一种通过挤压枪口内部来收紧霰弹枪枪口直径的枪械附件。收紧喉缩的松紧程度决定了弹丸散布，这对猎人很重要。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "smart choke"
msgid_plural "smart chokes"
msgstr[0] "智能喉缩"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Smart shotgun chokes are a breakthrough in modern firearms technology, "
"utilizing an electronic control system to automatically adjust the barrel in "
"different shooting situations. Through adaptive adjustments and data "
"analysis, it maintains the optimal performance of the muzzle to improve "
"ballistics and dramatically increase hit rates."
msgstr "智能霰弹枪喉缩是现代枪械技术的突破，利用电子控制系统在不同射击情况下自动调整枪管。通过自适应调整和数据分析，维持枪口的最佳性能以改善弹道并大幅提高命中率。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "neuro trigger"
msgid_plural "neuro trigger"
msgstr[0] "神经扳机"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"Reads the user's brainwaves to ensure that the firearm fires as intended, "
"eliminating reflex time and improving hit rates."
msgstr "读取使用者的脑电波，确保枪械按意图开火，消除反射时间并提高命中率。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "turbo charger"
msgid_plural "turbo chargers"
msgstr[0] "涡轮增压器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A high-powered accumulator that increases the output of a Gauss gun, "
"increasing its rate of fire. On the flip side, it significantly increases "
"the firearm's dispersion and recoil, making it more difficult to maneuver."
msgstr "一种高功率蓄能器，提升高斯枪的输出功率，增加射速。另一面是显著增加枪械散布和后坐力，使其更难操控。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "ammo transfer unit"
msgid_plural "ammo transfer units"
msgstr[0] "弹药传输单元"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A component required to permanently change a firearm's method of feeding "
"from a magazine to a 'transfer'. A tiny portal generator inside the device "
"opens and closes, pushing the ammunition 'one by one' into the firearm's "
"chamber, making it impossible to fire but eliminating the need to carry a "
"spare magazine. If you see this, it's a bug."
msgstr "用于永久将枪械供弹方式从弹匣改为传输模式的组件。装置内有一个微型传送门发生器，通过不断开合将弹药逐发推入枪膛，使其无法射击但无需携带备用弹匣。如果你看到这行说明，说明出bug了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "photon overcharger"
msgid_plural "photon overcharger"
msgstr[0] "光子超载器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"This is a custom capacitor part for the hardlight rifle that disables the "
"output limiter.  Overcharges photons, allowing you to fire a precise and "
"extremely powerful single shot."
msgstr "这是硬光步枪的定制电容器部件，禁用输出限制器。超载光子，让你能发射一发精准且极为强大的单发射击。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid "photon compressor"
msgid_plural "photon compressor"
msgstr[0] "光子压缩器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A custom capacitor component for the hardlight rifle, a modification that "
"compresses and solidifies photons. The densely compressed photon shells "
"explode on impact, scattering shrapnel like a grenade."
msgstr "硬光步枪的定制电容器部件，一种压缩和固化光子的改装。密集压缩的光子弹壳命中时爆炸，像榴弹一样散射碎片。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "portable Autodoc"
msgid_plural "portable Autodocs"
msgstr[0] "便携式自动医疗仪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'portable Autodoc'}
#. ~ Description for portable Autodoc
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight, highly compact autodoc seamlessly integrated with a foldable "
"camp cot. Its structural volume and weight have been drastically minimized "
"for maximum tactical portability, allowing survivalists to deploy a full "
"bionic surgical theater anywhere in the field. It remains a precise "
"apparatus used for the installation and removal of bionics, and is only as "
"skilled as its operator. Retrieve it by smashing it with the S key."
msgstr "一款轻便、高度紧凑的自动医疗机，与可折叠行军床无缝集成。其结构体积和重量已大幅优化以实现最大战术便携性，使幸存者能够在野外任何地方部署完整的仿生手术平台。它仍是一台用于安装和移除生化插件的精密设备，其技术水平仅取决于操作者。按S键砸毁即可回收。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "portable hydraulic press"
msgid_plural "portable hydraulic presses"
msgstr[0] "便携式液压机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'portable hydraulic press', 'str_pl': 'portable
#. hydraulic presses'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a portable version that dramatically reduces the size and weight of "
"conventional stationary hydraulic presses. It is constructed using a "
"hydraulic jack and is compact enough for survivors to carry by hand or load "
"into a vehicle. Although smaller in size, it delivers sufficient power to "
"crimp metal parts and form bullet casings."
msgstr "这是传统固定式液压机的便携版本，大幅缩减了尺寸和重量。它使用液压千斤顶构建，足够紧凑，幸存者可以手提或装入车辆。尽管体积较小，却能提供足够的力量来压接金属零件并成型弹壳。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "atomic forge"
msgid_plural "atomic forges"
msgstr[0] "原子锻造炉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'atomic forge'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is an atomic forge, powered by radioactive decay, that emits a pale blue "
"glow that is both terrifying and beautiful. It allows for the rapid "
"fabrication of graphene sheets and layered carbides. It doubles as a "
"refinery of sorts, and is the basis for the production of a variety of high-"
"tech components and raw materials."
msgstr "一台由放射性衰变驱动的原子熔炉，发出淡蓝色光芒，既令人畏惧又美丽。它可以快速制造石墨烯片和层压碳化物。同时兼作某种精炼设备，是生产各种高科技组件和原材料的基础。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "manipulator workbench"
msgid_plural "manipulator workbenches"
msgstr[0] "操控台"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'manipulator workbench', 'str_pl': 'manipulator
#. workbenches'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"This robotic arm with an arc welder and a large workbench with a large "
"touchscreen has everything you need. It can be used as a workbench to work "
"at twice the speed."
msgstr "这台配备电弧焊枪的机械臂和一个带大触摸屏的大型工作台，应有尽有。它可以作为工作台使用，制作速度翻倍。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "matter synthesizer: nanocompressor"
msgid_plural "matter synthesizer: nanocompressors"
msgstr[0] "物质合成器：纳米压缩机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'matter synthesizer: nanocompressor'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"A complex device for compressing raw materials and synthesising "
"nanomaterials. It is needed to make hydrogen containers, nanomaterials, "
"superalloys, and more, and includes a rapid cooler to compress gases and "
"fuels, and layered hydrocarbons for insulation."
msgstr "用于压缩原材料和合成纳米材料的复杂设备。用于制造氢气容器、纳米材料、超合金等，并包含快速冷却器以压缩气体和燃料，以及用于隔热的层压碳氢化合物。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "matter synthesizer: nano-precision sewing machine"
msgid_plural "matter synthesizer: nano-precision sewing machines"
msgstr[0] "物质合成器：纳米精密缝纫机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'matter synthesizer: nano-precision sewing
#. machine'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"A small, portable 3D printer capable of nanoscale processing, used to "
"engrave circuits on substrates. It can also be used as a kind of ''sewing "
"machine'' by drawing nanomaterials as thin as thread, so it can repair not "
"only fabrics but also layered carbides.  Furthermore, the fact that you can "
"input data into the machine and output all sorts of ultra-precise parts "
"suggests that you can probably even make CBMs. All of the previous steps are "
"also possible."
msgstr "小型便携式3D打印机，能进行纳米级加工，用于在基底上蚀刻电路。也可通过拉制细如丝线的纳米材料充当缝纫机，"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "portable CVD machine"
msgid_plural "portable CVD machines"
msgstr[0] "便携式CVD机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'portable CVD machine'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"You've taken a very expensive looking device that says \"Chemical Vapor "
"Deposition Machine\" and made it small by applied design.  If you put "
"certain very rare chemicals and elements into it, you could probably get a "
"diamond coating on your weapon. Remember: hydrogen + coal = smiley face."
msgstr "你把一台写着“化学气相沉积机”的昂贵设备通过应用设计缩小了。如果放入某些极稀有化学品和元素，你应该能给武器镀上钻石涂层。记住：氢气+煤炭=笑脸。"

#. ~ Description for portable CVD machine
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"We've taken a very expensive looking device that says \"Chemical Vapor "
"Deposition Machine\" and made it small by applied design.  If you put "
"certain very rare chemicals and elements into it, you could probably get a "
"diamond coating on your weapon. Remember: hydrogen + coal = smiley face. "
"Retrieve it by smashing it with the S key."
msgstr "我们把一台写着“化学气相沉积机”的昂贵设备通过应用设计缩小了。如果放入某些极稀有化学品和元素，你应该能给武器镀上钻石涂层。记住：氢气+煤炭=笑脸。按S键砸碎以回收。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "matter synthesizer: nanoprinter"
msgid_plural "matter synthesizer: nanoprinters"
msgstr[0] "物质合成器：纳米打印机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'matter synthesizer: nanoprinter'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"A miniature copy of a nanofabricator. Instead of a template, you can enter "
"your design directly or feed it into a small hole under the LCD panel and "
"print out the result. Inside this tiny factory are several 3D printers and a "
"robotic assembler, which can manufacture almost any non-organic object. Of "
"course, everything from the previous step can be made as well."
msgstr "一台纳米制造机的微型复制品。无需模板，你可以直接输入设计，或将其送入LCD面板下方的小孔中并打印结果。在这个微型工厂内部，有数台3D打印机和一个机器人装配器，几乎可以制造任何非有机物体。当然，前一步骤的所有物品也可制造。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid "stabilized portal"
msgid_plural "stabilized portals"
msgstr[0] "稳定传送门"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stabilized portal'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_main_tools.json
msgid ""
"As you gaze into the seemingly infinite depths of this portable hole in "
"reality, a phrase from a time forever gone echoes in your mind.  \\\"There "
"are two things that are infinite: the universe and human kleptomania.\\\""
msgstr "当你凝视这个便携式现实之洞看似无限的深处时，一句来自永恒往昔的话语在你脑海中回响。“有两样东西是无限的：宇宙和人类的盗窃癖。”"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "nanopackaged bandage"
msgid_plural "nanopackaged bandages"
msgstr[0] "纳米包装绷带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanopackaged bandage'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"An advanced bandage made of carbon fiber that has the ability to quickly "
"close wounds. The advanced nanotechnology inside this bandage has the "
"ability to quickly heal wounds while maintaining the proper pressure and "
"humidity needed for wound healing. This bandage also has the ability to "
"instantly increase your resilience, instantly restoring some health."
msgstr "一种由碳纤维制成的高级绷带，能够快速闭合伤口。绷带内部的高级纳米技术能在保持伤口愈合所需正确压力和湿度的同时快速愈合伤口。该绷带还能即时提升你的恢复力，立即恢复一些生命值。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "healing factor injector"
msgid_plural "healing factor injectors"
msgstr[0] "治愈因子注射器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'healing factor injector'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"A highly concentrated healing factor substance that closely resembles blood. "
"Embedded in a small pistol-shaped device used to inject advanced fast-"
"healing chemicals through the skin without using a needle. When used, it "
"greatly boosts healing abilities, instantly restoring a certain amount of "
"health. Use in a crisis."
msgstr "一种高度浓缩、酷似血液的治愈因子物质。装在一个小手枪形状的装置中，无需针头即可透过皮肤注射高级快速愈合化学物质。使用后可大幅提升愈合能力，立即恢复一定量的生命值。危机时刻使用。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "stamina juice"
msgid_plural "stamina juices"
msgstr[0] "耐力果汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stamina juice'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"Stamina juice. This triple blend of organic chemicals, including "
"electrolytes, is easy to drink and provides a noticeable endurance boost for "
"athletes and hard-working soldiers alike."
msgstr "耐力果汁。这种由电解质等有机化学物组成的三重混合物易于饮用，为运动员和辛勤士兵提供显著的耐力提升。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Stamina Regeneration"
msgstr "耐力再生"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "stamina elixir"
msgid_plural "stamina elixirs"
msgstr[0] "耐力灵药"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stamina elixir'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"Concentrated, randomly blended stamina juice. Can be used for energy in a "
"pinch, giving the user a burst of stamina recovery. I guess you could call "
"this a pseudo-stimpack."
msgstr "浓缩随机混合耐力果汁。可在紧急时刻提供能量，给予使用者一波耐力恢复。我想你可以把它称为伪兴奋剂。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Stamina Cascade"
msgstr "耐力奔涌"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Stamina Cascade'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Instantly restores your endurance significantly."
msgstr "立即显著恢复你的耐力。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Stamina Cascade'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "You'll feel energized from the inside out!"
msgstr "你会感到从内到外充满活力！"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "combat stimulant"
msgid_plural "combat stimulants"
msgstr[0] "战斗兴奋剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'combat stimulant'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"A combat stimulant, a field injectable drug that mixes powerful synthetic "
"adrenaline and endorphins with neuro-amplifying substances. It is contained "
"in a small, pistol-shaped device that is used to inject the advanced, fast-"
"recovery chemicals through the skin without the use of a needle. The use of "
"stimulants pushes the body's metabolic rate to an extreme, resulting in "
"faster reflexes and actions, which can help in intense combat."
msgstr "一种战斗兴奋剂，将强效合成肾上腺素和内啡肽与神经增强物质混合的战场注射药物。装在一个小手枪形状的装置中，无需针头即可透过皮肤注射高级快速恢复化学物质。使用兴奋剂将身体代谢率推向极限，带来更快的反应和行动速度，有助于激烈战斗。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Combat Stimulant Side Effects"
msgstr "战斗兴奋剂副作用"


#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Stimpack [1]"
msgstr "兴奋剂[1]"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Stimpack [1]'.
#. ~ Description of effect 'Stimpack [2]'.
#. ~ Description of effect 'Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "You can feel the battle stimulants coursing through the vein!"
msgstr "你能感受到战斗兴奋剂在血管中奔涌！"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Stimpack [2]"
msgstr "兴奋剂[2]"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Stimpack [3]"
msgstr "兴奋剂[3]"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Combat Stimulant Side Effects, Stimpack [1],
#. Stimpack [2], Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "The drug is coursing through your veins. Rip and Tear!"
msgstr "药物正在你血管中奔涌。撕碎他们！"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Combat Stimulant Side Effects, Stimpack [1],
#. Stimpack [2], Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "You're feeling depressed."
msgstr "你感到沮丧。"

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Combat Stimulant Side Effects, Stimpack [1],
#. Stimpack [2], Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"As the intensity of the stimulant wanes, you feel your body begin to strain."
msgstr "随着兴奋剂强度减弱，你感到身体开始承受压力。"

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Combat Stimulant Side Effects, Stimpack [1],
#. Stimpack [2], Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "It doesn't feel as strong and powerful as it used to."
msgstr "感觉不像之前那样强壮有力了。"

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Combat Stimulant Side Effects, Stimpack [1],
#. Stimpack [2], Stimpack [3]'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Ohhh, yeah."
msgstr "哦，是啊。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "simple sanitiser"
msgid_plural "simple sanitisers"
msgstr[0] "简易消毒剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'simple sanitiser'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"It's a desperate concoction of ingredients found in the wild to heal wounds "
"and stop or prevent infection. It may be suspect, but it may have healing "
"properties."
msgstr "一种用野外采集的原料拼凑而成的紧急混合物，用于愈合伤口并阻止或预防感染。也许令人怀疑，但可能具有疗愈特性。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "Tingling"
msgstr "刺痛"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Tingling'.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "It's stinging."
msgstr "正在发麻。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "insect jelly"
msgid_plural "insect jellies"
msgstr[0] "昆虫凝胶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'insect jelly', 'str_pl': 'insect jellies'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"A nutritious mass produced by insects. It has a sweet, mild flavor like "
"honey and a jelly-like texture."
msgstr "由昆虫生产的营养团块。味道甘甜温和如蜂蜜，质地呈凝胶状。"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'royal jelly', 'str_pl': 'royal jellies'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"It's a translucent, hexagonal lump of wax filled with a thick milky jelly. "
"It's filled with some of the most beneficial substances a hive can produce "
"since the apocalypse, treating many conditions and acting as an antidote."
msgstr "一种半透明六角形蜡块，内部充满浓稠的乳白色浆液。自灾变以来，它是蜂巢能产生的最有益物质之一，能治疗多种病症并充当解毒剂。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "royal jelly mixture"
msgid_plural "royal jelly mixtures"
msgstr[0] "蜂王浆混合物"


#. ~ Description for {'str': 'royal jelly mixture', 'str_pl': 'royal jelly
#. mixtures'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"A milky, sweet-smelling jelly that is mixed with a little triffid extract to "
"enhance the jelly's alchemical properties.  Cures all diseases."
msgstr "一种乳白色甜香气味的浆液，混入少量三尖树萃取物以增强其炼金特性。治疗所有疾病。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "triffid extract"
msgid_plural "triffid extracts"
msgstr[0] "三尖树萃取物"

#. ~ Description for triffid extract
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "An extract of fungal stings from a trifid plant."
msgstr "从三尖树植物中提取的真菌刺萃取物。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "triffid neutralizer"
msgid_plural "triffid neutralizers"
msgstr[0] "三尖树中和剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'triffid neutralizer'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"These are basically homemade potions that counteract harmful effects.  They "
"are effective against many known poisons, but may not be effective against "
"stronger poisons.  Treat and prevent biological poisons."
msgstr "这些基本上是自制的抵消有害效果的药剂。对大多数已知毒物有效，但可能对更强毒物无效。治疗并预防生物毒物。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "You feel an itch."
msgstr "你感到一阵痒。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "The toxin-removing effect is lost."
msgstr "毒素移除效果消失了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "The itching goes away."
msgstr "痒感消失了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "triffid antidote"
msgid_plural "triffid antidotes"
msgstr[0] "三尖树解毒剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'triffid antidote'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid ""
"A concentrated medical blend that detoxifies most known toxins and flushes "
"them out of the body.  It treats most harmful conditions and prevents them "
"for a period of time."
msgstr "一种浓缩的医用混合物，可解除大多数已知毒素并将其排出体外。治疗大多数有害状况并在一段时间内加以预防。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_meds.json
msgid "The toxin-removing effects of serum are lost."
msgstr "血清的毒素移除效果消失了。"

