#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "graphene sheet"
msgid_plural "graphene sheets"
msgstr[0] "石墨烯片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'graphene sheet', 'str_pl': 'graphene sheets'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"A thin polymeric carbon allotrope in which carbon atoms form a hexagonal "
"structure. Used to make materials with layered carbides."
msgstr "一种薄层聚合碳同素异形体，其中碳原子形成六角形结构。用于制造层压碳化物材料。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json .\miscs\sq_requirements.json
msgid "layered carbide"
msgid_plural "layered carbides"
msgstr[0] "层状碳化物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide', 'str_pl': 'layered carbides'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"Reinforced layered carbide armor plates, which can be used to craft or "
"repair high-tech equipment made of layered carbide."
msgstr "强化层压碳化物装甲板，可用于制作或修理由层压碳化物制成的高科技设备。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "vertigon"
msgid_plural "vertigons"
msgstr[0] "反重力素"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vertigon', 'str_pl': 'vertigons'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"It is an unknown mass of particles that possesses a bizarre property—defying "
"Earth’s gravity and constantly “falling” into the void—and emits a deep, "
"unstable amethyst-like purple glow. Even when simply held in one’s hand, an "
"unpleasant force field seems to pull the palm upward, while a nerve-grating, "
"subtle vibration seeps deep into the bones. This pale mass of particles, "
"which giant corporations regard as the heart of overtechnology, induces a "
"cosmic vertigo severe enough to tear apart a human’s semicircular canals "
"simply by being kept nearby without a shielding barrier. Perhaps these "
"particles possess a will of their own."
msgstr "一种未知粒子团，具有奇异的特性——违逆地球引力并持续向虚空坠落——散发出深邃不稳定的紫晶色紫光。即使简单处理也需要极度小心。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "bundle of layered carbides"
msgid_plural "bundles of layered carbides"
msgstr[0] "层状碳化物捆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bundle of layered carbides', 'str_pl': 'bundles
#. of layered carbides'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"Layered carbides, bundled tightly together for storage.  Activate or "
"disassemble to unpack."
msgstr "层状碳化物，紧密捆扎便于存放。激活或拆解以打开。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "enriched uranium canister"
msgid_plural "enriched uranium canisters"
msgstr[0] "浓缩铀罐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enriched uranium canister', 'str_pl': 'enriched
#. uranium canisters'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"A container containing enriched uranium that has been solidified by applying "
"pressure to uranium separated from the gas. It is highly radioactive and "
"must be handled with extreme care."
msgstr "一个装有浓缩铀的容器，通过对从气体中分离出的铀施加压力使其固化。具有极高放射性，必须极其小心地处理。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "depleted uranium"
msgid_plural "depleted uranium"
msgstr[0] "贫铀"






#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'depleted uranium'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"A byproduct of the processing of uranium. It is an extremely dense and "
"specialized heavy metal that can be used as a penetrator in combat firearms "
"or in armor."
msgstr "铀加工的副产品。一种极高密度的特殊重金属，可用作战斗枪械的侵彻体或用于装甲。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "uranium fuel cell"
msgid_plural "uranium fuel cells"
msgstr[0] "铀燃料电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'uranium fuel cell', 'str_pl': 'uranium fuel
#. cells'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"Fuel cells using uranium-235 and other compounds are capable of storing "
"enormous amounts of power and are a stable prototype concept. The uranium is "
"not used as fuel, but rather hydrogen is accelerated by the force of the "
"uranium and fused into helium to generate energy. This fuel cell is not "
"compatible with plutonium fuel cells."
msgstr "使用铀-235和其他化合物的燃料电池能够储存巨量电力，是一个稳定的原型概念。铀并非用作燃料，而是通过铀力加速氢来产生核聚变能量。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "monomolecular fiber"
msgid_plural "monomolecular fibers"
msgstr[0] "单分子纤维"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular fiber', 'str_pl': 'monomolecular
#. fibers'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"It's a very thin strand of carbon allotropes, superconducting, and "
"practically invisible to the eye. Be careful handling it so it doesn't fade!"
msgstr "一种极细的碳同素异形体丝线，具有超导性，肉眼几乎不可见。处理时要小心，别让它消失了！"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Type-Boy"
msgid_plural "Type-Boys"
msgstr[0] "Type-Boy"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Type-Boy', 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Tablet PC mode"
msgstr "平板电脑模式"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type-Boy', 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn on Tablet PC mode for your Type-Boy."
msgstr "你开启了Type-Boy的平板电脑模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Type-Boy', 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"It's a smart device that runs on UPS. A Type-Boy model from Fujin's "
"industry, it has the functionality of a smartwatch, plus a host of other "
"features and information, including maps and location tracking, a bionic "
"scanner, and a radiation biomonitor. These little computerized devices help "
"survivors perform a variety of tasks and manage information efficiently. You "
"can check it out by using."
msgstr "一款由UPS驱动的智能设备。富士工业出品的Type-Boy型号，具备智能手表功能以及大量其他特性和信息，包括地图和位置追踪、仿生扫描仪和辐射生物监测器。这些小型计算机化设备帮助幸存者高效执行各种任务和管理信息。使用以查看。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Type-Boy (tablet PC)"
msgid_plural "Type-Boys (tablet PC)"
msgstr[0] "Type-Boy（平板电脑）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Type-Boy (tablet PC)', 'str_pl': 'Type-
#. Boys (tablet PC)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Bionic scanner"
msgstr "仿生扫描仪"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type-Boy (tablet PC)', 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys
#. (tablet PC)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turned on your Type-Boy's bionic scanner mode."
msgstr "你开启了Type-Boy的仿生扫描仪模式。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'Type-Boy (tablet PC)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Type-Boys (tablet PC)'}.
#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'Type-Boys (bionic scanner)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys (bionic scanner)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "The Type-Boy's batteries are dead."
msgstr "Type-Boy的电池没电了。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Type-Boys (bionic scanner)"
msgid_plural "Type-Boys (bionic scanner)"
msgstr[0] "Type-Boy（仿生扫描仪）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Type-Boys (bionic scanner)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Type-Boys (bionic scanner)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Flashlight mode"
msgstr "手电筒模式"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type-Boys (bionic scanner)', 'str_pl': 'Type-
#. Boys (bionic scanner)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn on the flashlight mode for your Type-Boy."
msgstr "你开启了Type-Boy的手电筒模式。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "Type-Boy (flashlight)"
msgid_plural "Type-Boys (flashlight)"
msgstr[0] "Type-Boy（手电筒）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type-Boy (flashlight)', 'str_pl': 'Type-Boys
#. (flashlight)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn off your Type-Boy."
msgstr "你关闭了Type-Boy。"



#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic splint"
msgstr "仿生夹板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic splint'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A bionic splint helps your broken limb heal.  Your broken limb will heal 4x "
"faster."
msgstr "仿生夹板有助于骨折肢体愈合。骨折肢体将以4倍速度愈合。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic arm splint"
msgid_plural "bionic arm splints"
msgstr[0] "仿生手臂夹板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic arm splint'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic leg splint'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"Advanced splint. Less restrictive on limb movement, and quickly immobilizes "
"broken bones."
msgstr "高级夹板。对肢体活动限制较少，能快速固定骨折。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic leg splint"
msgid_plural "bionic leg splints"
msgstr[0] "仿生腿部夹板"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "binary sword"
msgid_plural "binary swords"
msgstr[0] "二进制剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'binary sword'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"Light and dark.  Black and white.  Life and death.  The Binary Sword holds "
"no middle ground as it turns your opponents OFF. The numbers 100111100 are "
"etched into the blade."
msgstr "光明与黑暗。黑与白。生与死。二进制剑不留中间地带，将你的对手直接关闭。剑身上蚀刻着数字100111100。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "monomolecular wire"
msgid_plural "monomolecular wires"
msgstr[0] "单分子线"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular wire'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A slender wire made of twisted monomolecular fibers. It's hard to handle "
"because it's a wire, but it can be easily concealed in a wrist or pocket, "
"making it an ideal assassination weapon."
msgstr "由单分子纤维拧成的细线。因为是线材所以难以操控，但可以轻松隐藏在手腕或口袋中，是理想的暗杀武器。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "carbon jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "碳纤维连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon jumpsuit'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from layers of graphene sheets that is "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It's one of the "
"essential pieces of gear for seasoned adventurers."
msgstr "由多层石墨烯片制成的轻薄全身服装，轻便、耐用且活动自如。是经验丰富冒险者的必备装备之一。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon insulation suit"
msgid_plural "carbon insulation suits"
msgstr[0] "碳纤维隔热服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon insulation suit'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from overlapping sheets of graphene that is "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It is one of the "
"essential pieces of equipment for seasoned adventurers exploring extreme "
"regions."
msgstr "由重叠石墨烯片制成的轻薄全身服装，轻便、耐用且活动自如。是探索极端地区的经验丰富冒险者的必备装备之一。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon full-body suit"
msgid_plural "carbon full-body suits"
msgstr[0] "碳纤维全身服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon full-body suit'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from layers of graphene sheets, it's "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It's one of the "
"essential pieces of gear for seasoned adventurers who don't want to give "
"away their identity."
msgstr "由多层石墨烯片制成的轻薄全身服装，轻便、耐用且活动自如。是不想暴露身份的经验丰富冒险者的必备装备之一。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "heat blade"
msgid_plural "heat blades"
msgstr[0] "热刃"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'heat blade'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You heat up the blade to bright red."
msgstr "你将刀刃加热至炽红。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heat blade'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A metal blade that is energized to generate high heat. This weapon can "
"easily cut through enemies with the sharpness of the blade and the force of "
"the high heat. Use to heat up the weapon."
msgstr "通电产生高温的金属刀刃。该武器以刀刃的锋利和高温的力量轻松切割敌人。使用以加热武器。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "heat blade (on)"
msgid_plural "heat blade (on)s"
msgstr[0] "热刃（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'heat blade (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turned off the heat blade."
msgstr "你关闭了热刃。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heat blade (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A metal blade that is electrically charged to generate high heat. This "
"weapon uses the sharpness of the blade and the power of the heat to cut "
"through enemies with ease. You'll feel a thrill of power as you draw the "
"weapon. Use to turn off the weapon."
msgstr "通电产生高温的金属刀刃。该武器以刀刃的锋利和高温的力量轻松切割敌人。拔刀时你会感受到力量的快感。使用以关闭武器。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "experimental hardlight blade (off)"
msgid_plural "experimental hardlight blade (off)s"
msgstr[0] "实验性硬光刀（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blade (off)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn on the hardlight blade."
msgstr "你开启了硬光刀。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blade (off)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"The Rivtech RMX-01 Experimental Hardlight Blade is a powerful weapon "
"utilizing laser technology, an eternal symbol of Jedi warriors, a fiery "
"testament to Newton, and the pinnacle of otaku science.  You can turn it on "
"using."
msgstr "Rivtech RMX-01实验性硬光刀是利用激光技术的强大武器，绝地武士的永恒象征，对牛顿的炽热证明，以及御宅科学的巅峰。使用以开启。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "experimental hardlight blades (on)"
msgid_plural "experimental hardlight blades (on)"
msgstr[0] "实验性硬光刀（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)'}.
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn off the hardlight blade."
msgstr "你关闭了硬光刀。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'experimental hardlight blades (on)'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"The Rivtech RMX-01 Experimental Hardlight Blade is a powerful weapon "
"utilizing laser technology, an eternal symbol of Jedi warriors, a fiery "
"testament to Newton, and the pinnacle of otaku science.  It can be turned "
"off by using."
msgstr "Rivtech RMX-01实验性硬光刀是利用激光技术的强大武器，绝地武士的永恒象征，对牛顿的炽热证明，以及御宅科学的巅峰。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "multi-chamber hydrogen bladder"
msgid_plural "multi-chamber hydrogen bladders"
msgstr[0] "多腔氢气囊"

#. ~ Description for multi-chamber hydrogen bladder
#. ~ Description for external multi-chamber hydrogen bladder
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'multi-chamber hydrogen bladder'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This invention serves as a living demonstration of why airships of the past "
"used helium instead of hydrogen—and why even those helium-filled airships "
"eventually faded into history. Packed a pouch made of graphene sheets to the "
"brim with hydrogen. Thanks to the honeycomb-shaped multi-wall structure, a "
"single peck from a bird won’t cause it to crash immediately, but staying "
"away from incendiary bombs or Molotov cocktails is the best way to preserve "
"both your life and the vehicle’s frame."
msgstr "这项发明生动证明了为什么过去的飞艇使用氦气而非氢气——以及为什么即使充氦飞艇也最终退出历史舞台。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external multi-chamber hydrogen bladder"
msgstr "外置多腔氢气囊"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity hover systems"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity hover systems"
msgstr[0] "反重力悬浮系统"

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity hover systems
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity hover systems', 'str_pl': 'anti-
#. gravity hover systems'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is a multipurpose anti-gravity thruster that replaces the wheels. It "
"glides effortlessly over swamps and ruins, defying the friction of the "
"earth. Countless corporate test pilots have been crushed against concrete "
"walls after losing control of this merciless hunk of metal."
msgstr "一种取代车轮的多用途反重力推进器。它无视地球的摩擦力，轻松滑过沼泽和废墟。无数企业试飞员在这块无情金属失控后撞上了混凝土墙。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity levitation module"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity levitation modules"
msgstr[0] "反重力悬浮模块"

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity levitation module
#. ~ Description for external anti-gravity levitation module
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity levitation module'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This anti-gravity subsystem utilizes the unstable force field of the "
"vertigon to effectively nullify the physical mass of vehicles weighing "
"several tons. A massive, heavily armored fortress equipped with this module "
"can glide effortlessly over swamps and ruins, as if made of feathers, "
"completely ignoring terrain penalties."
msgstr "该反重力子系统利用旋涡合金的不稳定力场，有效抵消重达数吨车辆的物理质量。搭载此模块的巨型重装甲堡垒可以如羽毛般轻松滑过沼泽和废墟，完全无视地形惩罚。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external anti-gravity levitation module"
msgstr "外置反重力悬浮模块"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity thruster"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity thrusters"
msgstr[0] "反重力推进器"

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity thruster
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity thruster'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is an inhumane propulsion system that generates immense acceleration by "
"channeling vertigon’s unstable repulsive field backward. The moment the "
"ignition switch is pressed, a murderous gravitational acceleration—seemingly "
"strong enough to shatter the backrest—threatens the pilot’s spine. However, "
"corporate accountants simply record the rupture of a pilot’s internal organs "
"as “acceptable operational losses” if this brute-force thrust can break "
"through enemy defenses."
msgstr "这是一种不人道的推进系统，通过向后引导反重力素的不稳定排斥场产生巨大加速度。按下点火开关瞬间，一股致命引力"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external anti-gravity thruster"
msgstr "外置反重力推进器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "vehicle manipulator workbench"
msgstr "车载机械臂工作台"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "cargo dimension"
msgstr "货舱维度"










#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mega freezer"
msgid_plural "mega freezers"
msgstr[0] "巨型冰箱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mega freezer', 'str_pl': 'mega freezers'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A large version of the 1000 litre capacity freezer designed as a mobile "
"solution for freezing food. It provides insulation from external elements."
msgstr "1000升容量冰箱的大型版本，设计为移动冷冻食物的解决方案。提供对外部元素的隔温保护。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mega freezer'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A large version of the 600 litre capacity freezer designed as a mobile "
"solution for freezing food. It provides insulation from external elements."
msgstr "600升容量冰箱的大型版本，设计为移动冷冻食物的解决方案。提供对外部元素的隔温保护。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "freezer dimension"
msgstr "冰柜维度"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "superfast recharging station"
msgid_plural "superfast recharging stations"
msgstr[0] "超快速充电站"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superfast recharging station'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is a state-of-the-art charging station that runs on vehicle power. "
"During operation, it will charge any rechargeable battery (cellular, lead-"
"acid, etc.) inserted into the internal storage compartment with ultra-fast "
"charging technology, much faster than a battery charging station. The unit "
"requires a pre-installed storage compartment to install, and can be switched "
"on and off from the dashboard or electronics controls."
msgstr "这是一台由车辆供能运行的最先进充电站。运行期间，它会使用超快充电技术对插入内部储物格的任何可充电电池（手机电池、铅酸电池等）进行充电，比电池充电站快得多。该装置需要预先安装储物格才能安装，可从仪表盘或电子控制系统开关。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "atomic engine"
msgid_plural "atomic engines"
msgstr[0] "原子引擎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'atomic engine'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A nuclear engine that generates electricity through radioactive decay to "
"provide continuous, reliable power for a vehicle. Thanks to its advanced "
"design, there is no wasted power when multiple are installed in a vehicle."
msgstr "一种通过放射性衰变发电的核引擎，为车辆提供持续可靠的动力。得益于其先进设计，车辆中安装多台时不会产生浪费的电力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted hardlight sidearm"
msgstr "车载硬光副武器"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted hardlight scatter gun"
msgstr "车载硬光散射枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted hardlight carbine"
msgstr "车载硬光卡宾枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted hardlight rifle"
msgstr "车载硬光步枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted hardlight precision rifle"
msgstr "车载硬光精确步枪"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "mounted tesla cannon"
msgstr "车载特斯拉炮"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "layered carbide plates"
msgid_plural "layered carbide plates"
msgstr[0] "层压碳化物板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide plates', 'str_pl': 'layered
#. carbide plates'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced, layered carbide plate that's lightweight yet strong; the best "
"bullet-stopper you can stick on a vehicle."
msgstr "一块强化层压碳化物板，轻便而坚固；你能装在车辆上的最佳防弹材料。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "layered carbide frame"
msgid_plural "layered carbide frames"
msgstr[0] "层压碳化物框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide frame'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "A large frame made of layered carbide."
msgstr "由层压碳化物制成的大型框架。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide frame'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A layered carbide frame. Other vehicle components can be mounted on it, and "
"it can be attached to other frames to increase the vehicle's size. "
msgstr "层压碳化物框架。其他车辆部件可安装其上，可连接其他框架以增加车辆尺寸。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "heavy-duty layered carbide frame"
msgid_plural "heavy-duty layered carbide frames"
msgstr[0] "重型层压碳化物框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy-duty layered carbide frame'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A large reinforced layered carbide frame used in the construction of "
"lightweight military vehicles."
msgstr "用于制造轻型军用车辆的大型强化层压碳化物框架。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy-duty layered carbide frame'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A relatively heavy layered carbide frame. Other vehicle components can be "
"mounted on it, and it can be attached to other frames to increase the "
"vehicle's size.  Increased mass makes it more resistant to damage in "
"collisions."
msgstr "相对沉重的层压碳化物框架。其他车辆部件可安装其上，可连接其他框架以增加车辆尺寸。增加的质量使其在碰撞中更能抵抗伤害。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide plates'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A strong layered carbide wall. Keeps zombies outside the vehicle and "
"prevents people from seeing through it."
msgstr "一面坚固的层压碳化物墙。将丧尸挡在车外并防止人们看穿。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "layered carbide quarterpanel"
msgstr "层压碳化物半隔板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide quarterpanel'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A half-height strong layered carbide wall. Keeps zombies outside the vehicle "
"but allows people to see over it."
msgstr "一面半高的坚固层压碳化物墙。将丧尸挡在车外但允许人们越过它看到外面。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "layered carbide roof"
msgstr "层压碳化物车顶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbide roof'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "A thick layered carbide roof."
msgstr "一块厚实的层压碳化物车顶。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "secret vertigon weapons engineering manual"
msgid_plural "secret vertigon weapons engineering manuals"
msgstr[0] "机密旋涡合金武器工程手册"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'secret vertigon weapons engineering manual',
#. 'str_pl': 'secret vertigon weapons engineering manuals'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"This is a thick, bound volume with a red warning label on the cover that "
"reads, “Unauthorized access strictly prohibited.” Inside, it is densely "
"packed with assembly diagrams for cutting-edge specialized firearms that "
"defy common sense, as well as manufacturing methods for their core "
"components. With the right tools and materials, you could build this "
"embodiment of dangerous technology yourself."
msgstr "这是一本厚重的装订卷，封面上有红色警告标签写着未经授权严禁访问。内部密密麻麻装满尖端特种装备的组装图解"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "overcharged stabilized portal"
msgid_plural "overcharged stabilized portals"
msgstr[0] "超载稳定传送门"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'overcharged stabilized portal'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"An industrialized, heavy-duty version of the stabilized portal. Reinforced "
"with vertigon to withstand massive dimensional pressure, it is incredibly "
"bulky and heavy, but is capable of swallowing an entire warehouse of loot."
msgstr "稳定传送门的工业化重型版本。用旋涡合金强化以承受巨大的维度压力，极其笨重，但足以吞下整座仓库的战利品。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "dreadnought cargo dimension"
msgstr "无畏级货运维度"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "tactical stabilized portal"
msgid_plural "tactical stabilized portals"
msgstr[0] "战术稳定传送门"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical stabilized portal'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"A masterpiece of dimensional engineering. Using vertigon to completely erase "
"its physical footprint, this tactical portal weighs practically nothing and "
"can be folded away in an instant."
msgstr "维度工程的杰作。使用旋涡合金完全抹去了物理存在感，这个战术传送门几乎零重量，可以瞬间折叠收纳。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "tactical cargo dimension"
msgstr "战术货运维度"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "spatial shimmer"
msgstr "空间微光"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "dimensional tear"
msgstr "维度撕裂"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "vertigon rupture"
msgstr "旋涡合金破裂"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm VCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"An advanced 9x19mm +P+ round treated with a vertigon coating that almost "
"entirely eliminates friction and air resistance. It unleashes the absolute "
"potential of the projectile, boasting improved damage and penetration over "
"conventional rounds."
msgstr "一种高级9x19mm +P+弹药，经过旋涡合金涂层处理，几乎完全消除了摩擦和空气阻力。释放弹丸的绝对潜能，与传统弹药相比具有更高的伤害和穿透力。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56x45mm VCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"An advanced 5.56x45mm HVP round treated with a vertigon coating that almost "
"entirely eliminates friction and air resistance. It unleashes the absolute "
"potential of the projectile, boasting improved damage and penetration over "
"conventional rounds."
msgstr "一种高级5.56x45mm HVP弹药，经过旋涡合金涂层处理，几乎完全消除了摩擦和空气阻力。释放弹丸的绝对潜能，与传统弹药相比具有更高的伤害和穿透力。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm VCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"An advanced 7.62x51mm HVP round treated with a vertigon coating that almost "
"entirely eliminates friction and air resistance. It unleashes the absolute "
"potential of the projectile, boasting improved damage and penetration over "
"conventional rounds."
msgstr "一种高级7.62x51mm HVP弹药，经过旋涡合金涂层处理，几乎完全消除了摩擦和空气阻力。释放弹丸的绝对潜能，与传统弹药相比具有更高的伤害和穿透力。"


#. ~ Description for {'str': '.50 BMG VCP'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"An advanced .50 BMG round treated with a vertigon coating that almost "
"entirely eliminates friction and air resistance. It unleashes the absolute "
"potential of the projectile, boasting improved damage and penetration over "
"conventional rounds."
msgstr "一种高级.50 BMG弹药，经过旋涡合金涂层处理，几乎完全消除了摩擦和空气阻力。释放弹丸的绝对潜能，与传统弹药相比具有更高的伤害和穿透力。"

#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid "vertigon coated uranium rail"
msgid_plural "vertigon coated uranium rails"
msgstr[0] "旋涡合金涂层铀轨弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vertigon coated uranium rail'}
#: .\items\advtech\sq_vertigon_tier.json
msgid ""
"This is a projectile for electromagnetic weapons, cast with a depleted "
"uranium core and finished with a vertigon coating. With its coefficient of "
"friction completely eliminated, it shatters any armor plate in a single "
"strike the moment it leaves the railgun muzzle."
msgstr "用于电磁武器的弹丸，以贫铀芯铸造，外覆旋涡合金涂层。摩擦系数被完全消除，离开电磁炮口的瞬间便能一击粉碎任何装甲板。"




#: .\items\item_common\sq_armor_override.json
msgid "fur blanket"
msgid_plural "fur blankets"
msgstr[0] "毛毯"




































#: .\items\item_common\sq_armor_override.json
msgid "windbreaker"
msgid_plural "windbreakers"
msgstr[0] "风衣"



























































#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "pack frame"
msgid_plural "pack frames"
msgstr[0] "背包框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pack frame'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"A device made to be carried by a person with a load on top of it. It is "
"quite heavy, but can carry a large amount of weight, making it a favorite of "
"caravaners."
msgstr "一种供人背负重物的装置。相当沉重，但能承载大量重量，深受商队喜爱。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "crude pack frame"
msgid_plural "crude pack frames"
msgstr[0] "简陋背包框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crude pack frame'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "A simple carrying device made of wooden sticks and string."
msgstr "用木棍和绳子制成的简易背负装置。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "pipe A-frame pack"
msgid_plural "pipe A-frame packs"
msgstr[0] "管材A型框架背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pipe A-frame pack'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"A carrying device made of welded pipe that provides some storage, and is "
"lightweight and sturdy."
msgstr "用焊接管道制成的背负装置，提供一定存储空间，轻便且坚固。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "steel carrier frame"
msgid_plural "steel carrier frames"
msgstr[0] "钢制负重框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel carrier frame'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"It's a large carrier made of steel.  It is very heavy, but equally strong."
msgstr "一个大型钢制负重架。非常沉重，但同样坚固。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "frame pack"
msgid_plural "frame packs"
msgstr[0] "框架背包"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frame pack'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"It's a cross between a large military backpack used by hikers and soldiers "
"and an A-shaped pipe holder that not only provides a large amount of storage "
"space, but also helps you carry heavy objects.  Wait, a pack frame with a "
"backpack? That's genius."
msgstr "这是徒步者和士兵使用的大型军用背包与A型管架的混合体，不仅提供大量存储空间，还能帮你搬运重物。等等，背包框架加背包？真是天才。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "rat-pack"
msgid_plural "rat-packs"
msgstr[0] "鼠背包"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rat-pack'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"This ultra-capacity backpack is made of multiple composite materials. It's "
"made to withstand a variety of impacts, and its ergonomic design makes it "
"much less restrictive than its bulk and weight. Not only does it hold three "
"weapons, but it also has room for your pet. Salute you for being a pack rat."
msgstr "这款超大容量背包由多种复合材料制成。能承受各种冲击，人体工学设计使其束缚感远低于其体积和重量应有的水平。不仅能存放三件武器，还能容纳你的宠物。致敬你这个囤积鼠。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "dimension stabilizer"
msgid_plural "dimension stabilizers"
msgstr[0] "维度稳定器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dimension stabilizer'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"An experimental storage unit connected to subspace. The portal is resonating "
"between two parallel coils."
msgstr "连接到子空间的实验性存储单元。传送门在两个平行线圈之间产生共振。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "power armor dimension stabilizer"
msgid_plural "power armor dimension stabilizers"
msgstr[0] "动力装甲维度稳定器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'power armor dimension stabilizer'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"Combined a power armor hauling frame with a dimensional stabilizer. Ah, what "
"a perfect idea."
msgstr "将动力装甲搬运框架与维度稳定器合二为一。啊，多么完美的构想。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "vanguard exoskeleton"
msgid_plural "vanguard exoskeletons"
msgstr[0] "先锋外骨骼"


#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'vanguard exoskeleton'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "The skeleton has run out of power."
msgstr "外骨骼电量耗尽。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vanguard exoskeleton'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"A military all-weather combat armored exoskeleton capable of storing "
"weapons. A robotic system of sorts that mechanically adds strength to the "
"wearer, with attached Kevlar armor plates that provide moderate defense, and "
"actuators that give a bonus to strength. Power up when used."
msgstr "一款军用全天候战斗装甲外骨骼，可存放武器。一种通过机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统，附有凯夫拉装甲板提供中等防御，驱动装置提供力量加成。使用时供能启动。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "vanguard exoskeleton (on)"
msgid_plural "vanguard exoskeletons (on)"
msgstr[0] "先锋外骨骼（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'vanguard exoskeleton (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'vanguard exoskeletons (on)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'sprinter skeleton (on)', 'str_pl': 'sprinter
#. skeletons (on)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'industrial exoskeleton (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'industrial exoskeletons (on)'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "The exoskeleton disengages."
msgstr "外骨骼已解除。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vanguard exoskeleton (on)', 'str_pl': 'vanguard
#. exoskeletons (on)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"A military all-weather combat armored exoskeleton capable of storing "
"weapons. A robotic system of sorts that mechanically adds strength to the "
"wearer, with Kevlar armor plates that provide decent defense, and actuators "
"that give bonuses to strength. It is currently operational, and is "
"constantly consuming power. Use to stop it from working."
msgstr "一款军用全天候战斗装甲外骨骼，可存放武器。一种通过机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统，凯夫拉装甲板提供良好防御，驱动装置提供力量加成。当前正在运行，持续消耗电力。使用以停止运行。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "sprinter exoskeleton"
msgid_plural "sprinter exoskeletons"
msgstr[0] "疾跑外骨骼"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'sprinter exoskeleton'}.
#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'industrial exoskeleton'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "The exoskeleton is insufficiently powered."
msgstr "外骨骼电力不足。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sprinter exoskeleton'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight reinforced exoskeleton with fast maneuverability. A type of "
"robotic system that mechanically adds strength to the wearer, and is "
"equipped with servo motors to aid in running, giving a bonus to movement "
"speed. Power up when used."
msgstr "一款具有快速机动能力的轻量强化外骨骼。一种通过机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统，配备伺服电机辅助奔跑，提供移动速度加成。使用时供能启动。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
