"A lightweight reinforced exoskeleton with fast maneuverability. A type of "
"robotic system that mechanically adds strength to the wearer, and is "
"equipped with servo motors to aid in running, giving a bonus to movement "
"speed. It is currently operational, and is constantly consuming power. Use "
"to stop working."
msgstr "一款具有快速机动能力的轻量强化外骨骼。一种通过机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统，配备伺服电机辅助奔跑，提供移动速度加成。当前正在运行，持续消耗电力。使用以停止工作。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
msgid "industrial exoskeleton"
msgid_plural "industrial exoskeletons"
msgstr[0] "工业外骨骼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'industrial exoskeleton'}
