"A type of armor developed for civilian use, it is a robotic system that "
"mechanically adds strength to the wearer, powered by hydraulics, motors, "
"pistons, etc. Power on when used."
msgstr "为民间使用开发的护甲类型，是一种通过液压、电机、活塞等机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统。使用时供能启动。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_cargo_frame.json
