"mechanically adds strength to the wearer, powered by hydraulics, motors, "
"pistons, etc. It is currently operating, and is constantly consuming power. "
"to stop working."
msgstr "为民间使用开发的护甲类型，是一种通过液压、电机、活塞等机械方式增强穿戴者力量的机器人系统。当前正在运行，持续消耗电力。使用以停止工作。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_generic.json
msgid "fool's gold loaf"
msgid_plural "fool's gold loaves"
msgstr[0] "愚人金面包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "fool's gold loaf", 'str_pl': "fool's gold
#. loaves"}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_generic.json
msgid ""
"This legendary sandwich involves hollowing out an entire loaf of white bread "
"and stuffing it with a jar of peanut butter, a jar of fruit jam, and a pound "
"of cooked bacon. A calorie bomb that Elvis Presley loved during his "
"lifetime, it offers immense satisfaction but will take a serious toll on "
"your blood vessels."
msgstr "这款传奇三明治是将一整条白面包挖空，塞入一罐花生酱、一罐果酱和一磅熟培根。这是埃尔维斯·普雷斯利生前钟爱的热量炸弹，带来极大满足感，但会对你的血管造成严重负担。"







