#: .\items\item_common\sq_generic.json
msgid "40x46mm shell-less grenade"
msgid_plural "40x46mm shell-less grenades"
msgstr[0] "40x46mm 无壳榴弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '40x46mm shell-less grenade'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_generic.json
msgid ""
"A 40x46mm shell-less, low velocity, dual-purpose high explosive grenade for "
"the Rivtech grenade launcher. It is a shell-less round and cannot be "
"disassembled or reused."
msgstr "用于Rivtech榴弹发射器的40x46mm无壳低速双用途高爆榴弹。由于是无壳弹，无法拆解或重复使用。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof canteen"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof canteens"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火水壶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof canteen'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A military-style water canteen with a 1.5 liter capacity, reinforced with "
"Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric.  Commonly worn at the hip."
msgstr "1.5升容量的军用风格水壶，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成。通常佩戴在臀部。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof harness"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof harnesses"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火背带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof harness', 'str_pl': 'survivor
#. fireproof harnesses'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built light harness reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric, covered with pouches and including an integral tactical "
"sling for a small rifle or other such weapon.  Durable and carefully crafted "
"to be comfortable to wear.  Activate to holster/draw your weapon."
msgstr "定制轻型背带，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，布满小袋并包含一条用于小型步枪或其他武器的集成战术背带。耐用且精心制作，佩戴舒适。激活以放入/拔出武器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof belt"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof belts"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火腰带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof belt'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built utility belt, reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric, covered with straps and pouches containing many useful "
"hand tools and a sheath to carry a smaller blade.  Durable and carefully "
"crafted to be comfortable to wear.  Activate to sheathe/draw a weapon."
msgstr "定制多功能腰带，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，布满绑带和小袋，装有各种实用手工具和一个携带小型刀片的刀鞘。耐用且精心制作，佩戴舒适。激活以收入/拔出武器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof headlamp"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof headlamps"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火头灯"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof headlamp'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"This is a custom-made LED headlamp reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric, to be more durable and with a more efficient battery "
"pack.  The adjustable strap allows it to be comfortably worn on your head or "
"attached to your helmet.  Use it to turn it on."
msgstr "定制LED头灯，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，更耐用且配备更高效电池组。可调节绑带可舒适地戴在头上或附着在头盔上。使用以开启。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof headlamp (on)"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof headlamps (on)"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火头灯（开启）"


#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof headlamp (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'survivor fireproof headlamps (on)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"This is a custom-made LED headlamp reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric, to be more durable, and with a more efficient battery "
"pack.  The adjustable strap allows it to be comfortably worn on your head or "
"attached to your helmet.  It is turned on, and continually draining "
"batteries.  Use it to turn it off."
msgstr "定制LED头灯，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，更耐用且配备更高效电池组。可调节绑带可舒适地戴在头上或附着在头盔上。已开启，持续消耗电池。使用以关闭。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor atomic fireproof headlamp"
msgid_plural "survivor atomic fireproof headlamps"
msgstr[0] "幸存者原子防火头灯"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor atomic fireproof headlamp'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"This is a custom-made, reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof "
"fabric headlamp powered by the magic of nuclear decay, focused for more "
"usable brightness.  The adjustable strap allows it to be comfortably worn on "
"your head or attached to your helmet.  Use it to close the cover and hide "
"the light."
msgstr "定制头灯，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，由核衰变魔法供能，聚焦出更实用的亮度。可调节绑带可舒适地戴在头上或附着在头盔上。使用以关闭灯罩并隐藏光线。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor atomic fireproof headlamp (covered)"
msgid_plural "survivor atomic fireproof headlamp (covered)"
msgstr[0] "幸存者原子防火头灯（遮罩）"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor atomic fireproof headlamp (covered)',
#. 'str_pl': 'survivor atomic fireproof headlamp (covered)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"This is a custom-made, reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof "
"fabric headlamp powered by the magic of nuclear decay, focused for more "
"usable brightness.  The adjustable strap allows it to be comfortably worn on "
"your head or attached to your helmet.  Use it to open the cover and show the "
"light."
msgstr "定制头灯，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，由核衰变魔法供能，聚焦出更实用的亮度。可调节绑带可舒适地戴在头上或附着在头盔上。使用以打开灯罩并显露光线。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof scabbard"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof scabbards"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火剑鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof scabbard'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A large, adjustable sheath reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric for holding swords and other large blades.  Activate to "
"sheathe/draw a weapon."
msgstr "大型可调节刀鞘，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，用于存放剑和其他大型刀片。激活以收入/拔出武器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof sheath"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof sheaths"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火刀鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof sheath'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A sheath reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric for "
"holding knives and other small blades.  It is easy to use without much "
"practice.  Activate to sheathe/draw a weapon."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的刀鞘，用于存放刀具和其他小型刀片。无需太多练习即可轻松使用。激活以收入/拔出武器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof ankle sheath"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof ankle sheaths"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火脚踝刀鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof ankle sheath'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A small concealed knife sheath reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex "
"fireproof fabric worn on the ankle.  It is awkward to use without practice.  "
"Activate to sheathe/draw a weapon."
msgstr "小型隐蔽刀鞘，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，佩戴在脚踝处。未经练习使用起来较为别扭。激活以收入/拔出武器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof baldric"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof baldrics"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火肩带剑鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof baldric'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A scabbard reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric, big "
"enough for anything up to a longsword, or even a bit larger than that.  "
"Designed to be worn at the waist, secured by a shoulder belt.  Activate to "
"sheath/draw a sword."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的剑鞘，大到足以容纳长剑甚至更大的武器。设计佩戴于腰间，由肩带固定。激活以收入/拔出剑。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof holster"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof holsters"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof holster'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A strap reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric worn on "
"the hip for holding pistol sized guns.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的绑带，佩戴于臀部，用于放置手枪大小的枪械。激活以放入/拔出枪械。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof bow sling"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof bow slings"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火弓背带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof bow sling'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A somewhat complicated set of straps and fabric, reinforced with Kevlar and "
"made of Nomex fireproof fabric to keep your bow close to hand and (mostly) "
"out of harms way.  Activate to holster/draw your bow."
msgstr "一套稍复杂的绑带和布料组合，凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成，使你的弓随手可得并（基本）不受伤害。激活以放入/拔出你的弓。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof axe ring holster"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof axe ring holsters"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火斧环套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof axe ring holster'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A combination of Kevlar and Nomex fireproof fabric and a metal ring to hold "
"an axe on your waist."
msgstr "凯夫拉与芳纶防火布料结合金属环，用于将斧头挂在腰间。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof spear strap"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof spear straps"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火长矛绑带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof spear strap'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A strap reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric tied "
"around the torso for toting spears while keeping your hands free.  You have "
"to duck to get through doors while one's in it, though.  Activate to holster/"
"draw a weapon."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的绑带，绑在躯干上用于携带长矛并解放双手。不过戴上后过门时需要弯腰低头。激活以放入/拔出武器。"

