#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof chest ammo pouch', 'str_pl':
#. 'survivor fireproof chest ammo pouches'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"An ammo pouch reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric that "
"can be strapped to your chest which is capable of holding a single magazine "
"or speedloader close at hand."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的弹药袋，可绑在胸前，能随手存放单个弹匣或快速装弹器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
