#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A small ammo pouch reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric "
"that can be strapped to your ankle which is capable of holding a single "
"small magazine or speedloader close at hand."
msgstr "小型凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的弹药袋，可绑在脚踝上，能随手存放单个小型弹匣或快速装弹器。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof ammo pouch"
