#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A small pouch reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric that "
"can be used to store most types of small ammunition, rockets will not fit.  "
"Activate to store ammunition."
msgstr "小型凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的袋子，可存放大多数小型弹药，火箭弹放不进去。激活以存放弹药。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "large survivor fireproof grenade pouch"
msgid_plural "large survivor fireproof grenade pouches"
msgstr[0] "大型幸存者防火榴弹袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large survivor fireproof grenade pouch',
#. 'str_pl': 'large survivor fireproof grenade pouches'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A pouch reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric for "
"holding up to four full-sized grenades of various types."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的袋子，可存放多达四枚各种类型的全尺寸榴弹。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof grenade pouch"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof grenade pouches"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火榴弹袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof grenade pouch', 'str_pl':
#. 'survivor fireproof grenade pouches'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A small pouch reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric for "
"storing cartridge grenades with straps for attaching it to your belt or "
"other webbing."
msgstr "小型凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的袋子，用于存放弹药榴弹，配有绑带可附着在腰带或其他织带上。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "XL survivor fireproof holster"
msgid_plural "XL survivor fireproof holsters"
msgstr[0] "XL幸存者防火枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL survivor fireproof holster'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A belt holster reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric "
"consisting of a loop and strap intended for use with larger firearms.  "
"Slightly more cumbersome than a standard holster due to the straps that hold "
"it flat against your leg, Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的腰带枪套，由环和绑带组成，适用于大型枪械。由于将枪套固定紧贴腿部的绑带，比标准枪套稍显笨重。激活以放入/拔出枪械。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof back holster"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof back holsters"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火背部枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof back holster'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A holster reinforced with Kevlar and made of Nomex fireproof fabric, big "
"enough for a rifle or other large gun.  Designed to be strapped to the "
"back.  Whilst initially cumbersome it becomes much easier to use with "
"practice.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "凯夫拉加固、芳纶防火布料制成的枪套，足够大以容纳步枪或其他大型枪械。设计绑在背后。起初较为笨重，随着练习会变得更容易使用。激活以放入/拔出枪械。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof duster"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof dusters"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火长外套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof duster'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A Kevlar armored custom full-length duster made of Nomex fireproof fabric, "
"covered with pouches and pockets.  Comfortable, durable, and great for "
"storage."
msgstr "凯夫拉装甲定制全长外套，芳纶防火布料制成，布满小袋和口袋。舒适、耐用，储物空间出色。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid "survivor fireproof trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "survivor fireproof trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "幸存者防火风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fireproof trenchcoat'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_nomex_survivor.json
msgid ""
"A Kevlar armored custom trenchcoat made of Nomex fireproof fabric, covered "
"with pouches and pockets.  Comfortable, durable, and great for storage."
msgstr "凯夫拉装甲定制风衣，芳纶防火布料制成，布满小袋和口袋。舒适、耐用，储物空间出色。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "plank shield"
msgid_plural "plank shields"
msgstr[0] "木板盾"

#. ~ Description for plank shield
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"It's wooden planks with a handle tied to it. It's clunky and heavy, but it "
"can fend off zombie attacks."
msgstr "用木板绑上把手做成的盾牌。笨重但能挡住丧尸的攻击。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "scrap shield"
msgid_plural "scrap shields"
msgstr[0] "废金属盾"

#. ~ Description for scrap shield
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"It's a metal plate with a handle made of pipe attached to it. It's sharp and "
"rusty, so you have to be careful when handling it."
msgstr "一块金属板，上面焊了根管子当把手。边缘锋利生锈，使用时要小心。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "round riot shield"
msgid_plural "round riot shields"
msgstr[0] "圆形防暴盾"

#. ~ Description for round riot shield
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A round, transparent plastic shield in the shape of a buckler, commonly used "
"by police and protesters. They are lightweight, strong, and comfortable to "
"use."
msgstr "小圆盾形状的透明塑料盾牌，警察和抗议者常用。轻便、坚固、使用舒适。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "riot shield"
msgid_plural "riot shields"
msgstr[0] "防暴盾"

#. ~ Use action msg for riot shield.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "The riot shield is pulled to a defensive posture!"
msgstr "防暴盾已转入防御姿态！"

#. ~ Description for riot shield
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A large square clear plastic shield commonly used by riot police.  Shaped "
"like the Roman scutum shield, it is designed to be worn in formation.  The "
"word ''police'' is emblazoned in large letters on the front. Use to raise "
"the shield."
msgstr "防暴警察常用的大型方形透明塑料盾牌。仿罗马方形盾设计，适合编队使用。正面印有大大的“POLICE”字样。使用以举起盾牌。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "riot shield (Def)"
msgid_plural "riot shields (Def)"
msgstr[0] "防暴盾（防御）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'riot shield (Def)', 'str_pl': 'riot shields
#. (Def)'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "The riot shield is lowered."
msgstr "防暴盾已放下。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'riot shield (Def)', 'str_pl': 'riot shields
#. (Def)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A square clear plastic shield commonly used by police and protesters.  "
"Shaped like the Roman scutum shield, it is designed to be worn in "
"formation.  The word ''police'' is emblazoned in large letters on the "
"front.  It is currently being used, and slowing you down.  Use to lower the "
"shield."
msgstr "方形透明塑料盾牌，警察和抗议者常用。仿罗马方形盾设计，适合编队使用。正面印有大大的“POLICE”字样。当前正在使用，会减慢你的速度。使用以放下盾牌。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "tactical shield: commando"
msgid_plural "tactical shields: commando"
msgstr[0] "战术盾牌：突击"



#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical shield: commando', 'str_pl': 'tactical
#. shields: commando'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"This shield offer high performance protection and magazine storage. If you "
"don't know what to choose, the tactical shield: commando is the best choice. "
"It's quite heavy but effective."
msgstr "这款盾牌提供高性能防护和弹匣存储空间。如果不知道该选什么，战术盾牌：突击是最佳选择。相当沉重但十分有效。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "tactical shield: bastion"
msgid_plural "tactical shields: bastion"
msgstr[0] "战术盾牌：堡垒"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tactical shield: bastion', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: bastion'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "The tactical shield is pulled to a defensive posture!"
msgstr "战术盾牌已转入防御姿态！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical shield: bastion', 'str_pl': 'tactical
#. shields: bastion'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A ballistic shield designed to allow the point man and anyone standing "
"behind it to safely approach their target. It is heavy and somewhat "
"cumbersome, but its protection cannot be denied.  Activate it to be held "
"close and in front of you."
msgstr "一种防弹盾牌，旨在让尖兵和身后的人安全接近目标。沉重且有些笨重，但其防护力无可否认。激活以将其紧握在身前。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "tactical shield: bastion (Def)"
msgid_plural "tactical shields: bastion (Def)"
msgstr[0] "战术盾牌：堡垒（防御）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tactical shield: bastion (Def)', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: bastion (Def)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tactical shield: frontline (Atk)', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: frontline (Atk)'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "The tactical shield is lowered."
msgstr "战术盾牌已放下。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical shield: bastion (Def)', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: bastion (Def)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A ballistic shield designed to allow the point man and anyone standing "
"behind it to safely approach their target. It is heavy and somewhat "
"cumbersome, but its protection cannot be denied. It is currently being used, "
"and slowing you down."
msgstr "一种防弹盾牌，旨在让尖兵和身后的人安全接近目标。沉重且有些笨重，但其防护力无可否认。当前正在使用，会减慢你的速度。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "tactical shield: frontline"
msgid_plural "tactical shields: frontline"
msgstr[0] "战术盾牌：前线"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tactical shield: frontline', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: frontline'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "The tactical shield is pulled to a assault posture!"
msgstr "战术盾牌已转入突击姿态！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical shield: frontline', 'str_pl': 'tactical
#. shields: frontline'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A shield that allows you to use a two-handed weapon while equipped with a "
"shield. The downside is that it leaves the holder's legs exposed.  Activate "
"it to be extended and held close in front of you."
msgstr "允许在装备盾牌的同时使用双手武器。缺点是会暴露持有者的双腿。激活以将其展开并紧握在身前。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid "tactical shield: frontline (Atk)"
msgid_plural "tactical shields: frontline (Atk)"
msgstr[0] "战术盾牌：前线（攻击）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tactical shield: frontline (Atk)', 'str_pl':
#. 'tactical shields: frontline (Atk)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_shields.json
msgid ""
"A shield that allows you to use a two-handed weapon while equipped with a "
"shield. The downside is that it leaves the holder's legs exposed. It is "
"currently being used, and slowing you down."
msgstr "允许在装备盾牌的同时使用双手武器。缺点是会暴露持有者的双腿。当前正在使用，会减慢你的速度。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid "simple patchwork scarf: olive"
msgid_plural "simple patchwork scarves: olive"
msgstr[0] "简易拼布围巾：橄榄绿"




#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
