#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nomad harness', 'str_pl': 'nomad harnesses'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built lightweight set of weight distributing pouches over your "
"entire body. Its cunningly placed and stabilized pockets can store a "
"remarkable amount of useful stuff without getting in the way or sacrificing "
"balance. Has a flashlight mounted on the shoulder and an internal reservoir "
"for water purification in the field, both exclusively powered by your "
"internal bionic energy."
msgstr "一套定制轻量负重分布袋，覆盖全身。巧妙布置且稳定的口袋可以存放大量实用物品，不妨碍行动也不影响平衡。肩部装有手电筒，并内置野外净水储水器，两者均完全由你的内部仿生能量供能。"

