#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid "advanced nomad suit"
msgid_plural "advanced nomad suits"
msgstr[0] "高级游牧服"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'advanced nomad suit'}.
#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid "You turn the climate control on."
msgstr "你开启了气候控制。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced nomad suit'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced but airy jumpsuit designed to survive the long-term wear and "
"tear of exploring the apocalyptic wasteland.  Rather than advanced polymer "
"fabrics which may not be available in many worlds, it is made of breathable "
"twill fabric with leather reinforcements ensuring it can be produced easily "
"regardless of technology level.  Its clever construction adds additional "
"core support, helping you to carry more equipment.  A set of cooling tubes "
"run throughout the clothing as well."
msgstr "一件经过加固但透气的连体服，专为在末日废土中长期探索的磨损而设计。不使用在许多世界中可能无法获得的高级聚合物面料，而是采用透气斜纹布配合皮革加固，确保无论技术水平如何都能轻松制作。巧妙的构造提供额外的核心支撑，帮助你携带更多装备。衣内还遍布一套冷却管道。"

#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid "advanced nomad suit (on)"
msgid_plural "advanced nomad suits (on)"
msgstr[0] "高级游牧服（开启）"


#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced nomad suit (on)', 'str_pl': 'advanced
#. nomad suits (on)'}
#: .\items\item_common\sq_suit.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced but airy jumpsuit designed to survive the long-term wear and "
"tear of exploring the apocalyptic wasteland. Rather than advanced polymer "
"fabrics which may not be available in many worlds, it is made of breathable "
"twill fabric with leather reinforcements ensuring it can be produced easily "
"regardless of technology level. Its clever construction adds additional core "
"support, helping you to carry more equipment. The internal cooling tubes are "
"active and humming."
msgstr "一件经过加固但透气的连体服，专为在末日废土中长期探索的磨损而设计。不使用在许多世界中可能无法获得的高级聚合物面料，而是采用透气斜纹布配合皮革加固，确保无论技术水平如何都能轻松制作。巧妙的构造提供额外的核心支撑，帮助你携带更多装备。内部冷却管道正在运行并发出嗡鸣。"

