#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mech: explorer (ride mode)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive mech: explorer (ride mode)'}
#: .\monsters\sq_mechs.json
msgid ""
"An standardized multi-role mech drone with a modified military "
"reconnaissance exoskeleton system and a drone authorized for autonomous "
"behavior. A loadout centered around optical weapons, it features average "
"melee capabilities and strong energy projection. You may be able to hack it "
"to accept you as its pilot.  Like all mech-suits it can act as a UPS from "
"its large battery."
msgstr "一款标准化多用途机甲无人机，配备改装军用侦察外骨骼系统，经授权可自主行动。以光学武器为核心的装备配置，具有平均的近战能力和强大的能量投射力。你可能可以黑入它以接受你作为驾驶员。与所有机甲服一样，可以通过其大型电池充当UPS。"

