#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive mech: explorer (standalone mode)'}
#: .\monsters\sq_mechs.json
msgid ""
"An standardized multi-role mech drone with a modified reconnaissance "
"exoskeleton system and a drone authorized for autonomous behavior. The "
"loadout is centered around optical weapons, with average melee capabilities "
"and strong energy projection. It is capable of operating unattended, but can "
"also be equipped with a pilot to increase its engagement capabilities."
msgstr "一款标准化多用途机甲无人机，配备改装侦察外骨骼系统，经授权可自主行动。以光学武器为核心的装备配置，具有平均的近战能力和强大的能量投射力。可无人值守操作，也可搭载驾驶员以增强作战能力。"

