#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mech: stronghold (ride mode)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive mech: stronghold (ride mode)'}
#: .\monsters\sq_mechs.json
msgid ""
"A localized defense/siege combat mech drone with a modified military combat "
"exoskeleton system and authorized autonomous behavior. It is a loadout "
"centered around live weapons, with average melee capabilities and strong "
"firepower projection. It can be likened to a walking tank. You may be able "
"to hack it to accept you as its pilot.  Like all mech-suits it can act as a "
"UPS from its large battery."
msgstr "一款局部防御/攻城作战机甲无人机，配备改装军用战斗外骨骼系统，经授权可自主行动。以实弹武器为核心的装备配置，具有平均的近战能力和强大的火力投射力。可被比作步行坦克。你可能可以黑入它以接受你作为驾驶员。与所有机甲服一样，可以通过其大型电池充当UPS。"

