#: .\monsters\sq_mechs.json
msgid ""
"A quadrupedal maneuverable mech drone with a modified military "
"reconnaissance exoskeleton system and a drone authorized for autonomous "
"behavior. A melee weapon-centric loadout, it is characterized by excellent "
"close combat capabilities and a high degree of mobility. It has a giant wolf-"
"like form, and its inhuman movement makes it excellent in close combat. You "
"may be able to hack it to accept you as its pilot.  Like all mech-suits it "
"can act as a UPS from its large battery."
msgstr "一款四足高机动性机甲无人机，配备改装军用侦察外骨骼系统，经授权可自主行动。以近战武器为核心的装备配置，具有卓越的近身作战能力和高度机动性。拥有巨型狼形外观，其非人的动作使它在近战中表现出色。你可能可以黑入它以接受你作为驾驶员。与所有机甲服一样，可以通过其大型电池充当UPS。"

