"Used to give frost-shooting monster a specific degree of inaccuracy. If you "
"encounter one of these in the wild, it's a bug."
msgstr "用于给发射冰霜的怪物提供特定程度的不准确性。如果在野外遇到这个，那是bug。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_monster_spells.json
msgid "frost fire breath"
msgid_plural "frost fire breaths"
msgstr[0] "霜火吐息"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_monster_spells.json
msgid ""
"Used to give ice-breathing bosses a specific degree of inaccuracy. If you "
"encounter one of these in the wild, it's a bug."
msgstr "用于给喷吐冰霜的Boss提供特定程度的不准确性。如果在野外遇到这个，那是bug。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_monster_spells.json
msgid "Permafrost Wind"
msgstr "永冻之风"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Permafrost Wind'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_monster_spells.json
msgid "Unleashes bone-chilling wind of absolute zero temperatures."
msgstr "释放绝对零度的刺骨寒风。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Permafrost Wind'}'
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'permafrost dragon', 'str_pl':
#. 'permafrost dragons'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_monster_spells.json zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "Chilly wind is gathering around the permafrost dragon!"
msgstr "寒风正在永冻龙周围聚集！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frozen zombie"
msgid_plural "frozen zombies"
msgstr[0] "冰冻丧尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frozen zombie'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A zombie stiffened by the biting cold. It moves significantly slower, but "
"its frozen flesh is harder to cut through."
msgstr "一具被刺骨寒冷冻僵的丧尸。行动显著变慢，但冻硬的肉体更难被切开。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frost zombie"
msgid_plural "frost zombies"
msgstr[0] "霜冻丧尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost zombie'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"Covered entirely in a thick layer of ice, this zombie is heavily armored "
"against physical attacks but moves at a glacial pace. Its touch saps the "
"warmth directly from your body. Those who succumb to its grasp simply join "
"the frozen march of the forgotten."
msgstr "全身覆盖厚冰层，对物理攻击有厚重护甲但移动极其缓慢。触碰直接汲取你身体的温度。那些屈服于其掌控的人只会加入被遗忘者的冰冻行军。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "ice brute"
msgid_plural "ice brutes"
msgstr[0] "冰霜蛮兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice brute'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A massive brute reinforced by thick glaciers of ice fused to its muscles. "
"Its devastating punches shatter walls and freeze bones. It swings with the "
"blind fury of a tortured soul, forever trapped within a tomb of its own "
"frozen flesh."
msgstr "一具被厚实冰川强化融合至肌肉的巨型蛮兽。毁灭性的拳头粉碎墙壁、冻结骨骼。它以一个受折磨灵魂的盲目狂怒挥舞双拳，永远被困在自身冰冻血肉的坟墓中。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frost nipper"
msgid_plural "frost nippers"
msgstr[0] "霜咬犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost nipper'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A canine corpse coated in frost. It's slightly bulkier than a normal zombie "
"dog, and its bite leaves a lingering, numbing chill. Even the loyalty of "
"man's best friend is corrupted by the biting, uncaring frost."
msgstr "一具覆满霜冻的犬尸。比普通丧尸犬略壮，咬伤会留下持续麻木的寒意。就连人类最好朋友的忠诚也被这刺骨无情的寒霜所腐蚀。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frost biter"
msgid_plural "frost biters"
msgstr[0] "霜噬犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost biter'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"An evolved, heavily armored ice hound. Its fangs are literal icicles capable "
"of piercing armor, delivering debilitating frostbite with every strike. "
"Driven by an insatiable hunger for warmth, it relentlessly hunts those who "
"still harbor the fading embers of life."
msgstr "进化后的重甲冰犬。其獠牙是真正的冰柱，能穿透护甲，每次攻击都会造成致残的冻伤。出于对温暖的无尽渴望，它无情地猎杀那些仍怀有生命余烬的人。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frost beast"
msgid_plural "frost beasts"
msgstr[0] "霜兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost beast', 'str_pl': 'frost beasts'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"An angular, icy horror that seems to slide between the falling snow. It "
"shatters the air around it, creating lesser, fragile reflections of itself "
"made of pure ice to hunt you down. Born from the deepest abyss of the frozen "
"wastes, it is a living testament to the world's creeping death."
msgstr "一头棱角分明的冰霜恐怖造物，似乎在飘雪间滑行。它粉碎周围的空气，创造出由纯冰构成的自身脆弱复制体来猎杀你。诞生于冰冻废土最深的深渊，它是世界蔓延死亡的活证。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'frost beast', 'str_pl': 'frost
#. beasts'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "The frost beast shatters reality, leaving a reflection in the ice!"
msgstr "霜兽粉碎了现实，在冰中留下了一个镜像！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "frost beast reflection"
msgid_plural "frost beast reflections"
msgstr[0] "霜兽镜像"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost beast reflection', 'str_pl': 'frost beast
#. reflections'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A fragile, identical copy of a frost beast formed entirely out of compacted "
"snow and ice. It melts away quickly if dealt enough damage. A fleeting "
"illusion born of abyssal frost, doomed to shatter and fade into the "
"unforgiving winter."
msgstr "由压实冰雪构成的霜兽脆弱复制体。受到足够伤害后会迅速融化。深渊之霜诞生的短暂幻象，注定粉碎并消逝于无情的寒冬。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "snowman"
msgid_plural "snowmen"
msgstr[0] "雪人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snowman', 'str_pl': 'snowmen'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A seemingly innocent snowman, animated by some unknown dark force. It's "
"extremely fragile to physical trauma and fire, but its snowy touch is bone-"
"chilling. A hollow mockery of childhood joy, shaped by the malice of the "
"cold."
msgstr "一个看似无害的雪人，被某种未知黑暗力量所驱动。对物理创伤和火焰极为脆弱，但其冰冷的触碰刺骨至极。寒冷恶意塑造的对童年欢乐的空洞嘲讽。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "ice golem"
msgid_plural "ice golems"
msgstr[0] "冰魔像"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice golem', 'str_pl': 'ice golems'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A towering construct of solid ice. While still vulnerable to blunt force and "
"fire, its sheer mass makes it incredibly tough to bring down. A mindless "
"sentinel molded from the frozen wastes, it crushes all warmth beneath its "
"unyielding weight."
msgstr "一尊由坚冰构成的巍峨造物。虽仍怕钝击和火焰，但其庞大质量使其极难击倒。由冰冻废土塑就的无心智哨兵，以不屈的重量碾碎一切温暖。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "Mr. Stabby"
msgid_plural "Mr. Stabbys"
msgstr[0] "刺刺先生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mr. Stabby'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A sinister snowman wearing a blood-stained red scarf, wielding an incredibly "
"sharp icicle shaped like a dagger. It is startlingly lethal in close "
"quarters. The crimson stains upon its scarf whisper of countless lives "
"snuffed out in the silent, uncaring snow."
msgstr "一个戴着染血红围巾的邪恶雪人，手持一把匕首形状的锋利冰柱。在近战中惊人致命。围巾上的深红污渍低语着无数生命在寂静无情的雪中被扼杀的故事。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "snow gangster"
msgid_plural "snow gangsters"
msgstr[0] "雪匪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snow gangster'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A snowman sporting a sharp fedora. One of its stick arms has been replaced "
"by a fully functional submachine gun made of black ice. A bizarre "
"manifestation of human violence, frozen in time and armed for indiscriminate "
"slaughter."
msgstr "一个戴着利落软呢帽的雪人。其中一根树枝手臂被一把功能完好的黑冰冲锋枪取代。人类暴力的奇异化身，冻结在时间里，全副武装只为无差别屠杀。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "The snow gangster sprays a hail of ice bullets!"
msgstr "雪匪扫射出一阵冰弹之雨！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "ice elemental"
msgid_plural "ice elementals"
msgstr[0] "冰元素"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice elemental'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A floating, jagged chunk of ice possessed by a malevolent spirit. It attacks "
"from a distance, hurling shards of freezing ice while dropping the "
"temperature around it. It is the cold will of the abyss given form, bearing "
"ancient grudges against those who dare to kindle the flame."
msgstr "一块被恶灵附体的锯齿状浮冰块。从远处攻击，投掷冰冻碎片的同时降低周围温度。它是深渊冰冷意志的具现，对敢于点燃火焰之人怀有古老的怨恨。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "The ice elemental hurls a freezing shard!"
msgstr "冰元素投出一枚冰冻碎片！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "ice demon"
msgid_plural "ice demons"
msgstr[0] "冰魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice demon'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"A terrifying apex elemental of frost. It generates a ferocious local "
"blizzard and boasts both devastating melee strikes and lethal long-range ice "
"blasts. To face it is to gaze into the heart of the creeping dark, where "
"neither hope nor fire can endure. It seeks only to plunge the world into an "
"eternal, silent slumber."
msgstr "霜冻的恐怖顶点元素。能产生猛烈的局部暴风雪，兼具毁灭性的近战打击和致命的远程冰爆。面对它就是凝视蔓延黑暗的核心，那里既无希望也无火焰可以存续。它只求将世界投入永恒的沉寂长眠。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "The ice demon unleashes a relentless barrage of freezing shards!"
msgstr "冰魔释放出无情的冻片弹幕！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "winter waker"
msgid_plural "winter wakers"
msgstr[0] "冬日唤醒者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'winter waker'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"An avatar of winter's cruelty. This walking blizzard radiates an intense, "
"sweeping aura of sub-zero temperatures, freezing the very air it walks "
"through. It wanders the desolate lands like a grieving monarch, "
"extinguishing the last remaining sparks of warmth in a dying world."
msgstr "寒冬残酷的化身。这团行走的暴风雪散发出强烈的零下温度横扫光环，冻结所经之处的空气。它像一位悲痛的君主徘徊在荒芜之地，熄灭垂死世界中最后的温暖火花。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'winter waker'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"The winter waker traces a freezing rune in the air, and ice blooms directly "
"upon your skin!"
msgstr "冬日唤醒者在空中划出一道冰封符文，冰霜直接在你皮肤上绽放！"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "permafrost dragon"
msgid_plural "permafrost dragons"
msgstr[0] "永冻龙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'permafrost dragon', 'str_pl': 'permafrost
#. dragons'}
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid ""
"An absolute nightmare of undeath and ice. Its colossal decaying body "
"radiates a chilling aura that freezes the blood in your veins. A single "
"breath from its maw spells absolute zero annihilation. Once a proud "
"sovereign of the skies, it was swallowed by the abyssal cold, its soul "
"hollowed out by ancient sins. Now, it stands as the ultimate harbinger of "
"the final winter, a tragic monument to the fading of the world. Gaze upon "
"it, and witness the death of fire."
msgstr "不死与寒冰的绝对噩梦。其巨大的腐烂身躯散发冻结血管的冰冷光环。口中一次吐息便是绝对零度的湮灭。曾是天空的骄傲君主，被深渊寒冷吞噬，灵魂被远古罪孽掏空。如今，它作为最终寒冬的至高先驱屹立，是世界凋零的悲剧丰碑。凝视它，见证火焰之死。"

#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter.json
msgid "The permafrost dragon exhales a devastating cone of absolute zero!"
msgstr "永冻龙喷出毁灭性的绝对零度锥形吐息！"





#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter_effects.json
msgid "Freezing"
msgstr "冻结"


#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter_effects.json
msgid "Frostnip"
msgstr "冻麻"


#.
#. ~ Speed name of effect(s) 'Frostnip, Frostbite'.
#: .\monsters\winter zeds\sq_zed-winter_effects.json
msgid "Frostbite"
msgstr "冻伤"


#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fleet-footed serum"
msgid_plural "Fleet-footed serums"
msgstr[0] "捷足血清"

#. ~ Description for Fleet-footed serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will make you a little faster on flat surfaces."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你在平地上移动得更快一些。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Plant threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Plant threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "植物阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Plant threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more plant-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像植物的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insect threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Insect threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "昆虫阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Insect threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more insect-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像昆虫的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Spider threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Spider threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "蜘蛛阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Spider threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more arachnid-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像蜘蛛的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Slime threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Slime threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "黏液阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Slime threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more slime-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像黏液的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fish threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Fish threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "鱼类阈值血清"

