#. ~ Description for Practised sleeper serum
#. ~ Description for Toxic skin serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will make you capable of falling asleep just about anywhere, if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。使你几乎能在任何地方入睡，前提是你的身体支持。"

