msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你更能抵抗疼痛。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Nightvision serum"
msgid_plural "Nightvision serums"
msgstr[0] "夜视血清"

#. ~ Description for Nightvision serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Makes your "
"eyes a little more sensitive to light in low-light situations, granting a "
"weak nightvision."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的眼睛在弱光环境中对光线更敏感，获得微弱的夜视能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
