msgstr[0] "毒抗血清"

#. ~ Description for Poison resistance serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will make you more resistant to poisons."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你更能抵抗毒素。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Sheer bulk serum"
msgid_plural "Sheer bulk serums"
msgstr[0] "强壮体格血清"

#. ~ Description for Sheer bulk serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"makes you develop a very robust build."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你发育出非常结实的体魄。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Immense bulk serum"
msgid_plural "Immense bulk serums"
msgstr[0] "巨人体格血清"

#. ~ Description for Immense bulk serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"makes you develop an incredibly robust build to such extent that you would "
"not be allowed to compete in pre-Cataclysm sports."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你发育出极端强健的体格，以至于灾变前的体育比赛会禁止你参赛。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Tough serum"
msgid_plural "Tough serums"
msgstr[0] "坚韧血清"

#. ~ Description for Tough serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"hardens your bones and muscles, increasing the amount of hits you can take."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。硬化你的骨骼和肌肉，提升你能承受的攻击次数。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Durability serum"
msgid_plural "Durability serums"
msgstr[0] "耐久血清"

#. ~ Description for Durability serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"further enhances your body's durability beyond simple toughness."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在简单坚韧的基础上进一步增强身体的耐久力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Unbreakable serum"
msgid_plural "Unbreakable serums"
msgstr[0] "不坏血清"

#. ~ Description for Unbreakable serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Basically "
"super soldier body durability."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。基本上就是超级士兵级的身体耐久力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Thick skin serum"
msgid_plural "Thick skin serums"
msgstr[0] "厚皮血清"

#. ~ Description for Thick skin serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. It "
"thickens your skin and gives you some resistance to being cut."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。加厚你的皮肤，并赋予你对切割的一定抵抗力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Strong back serum"
msgid_plural "Strong back serums"
msgstr[0] "强背血清"

#. ~ Description for Strong back serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. With this "
"your spine reinforces itself and you become capable of carrying heavier "
"loads."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的脊柱得到强化，使你能够携带更重的负载。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Strong stomach serum"
msgid_plural "Strong stomach serums"
msgstr[0] "强胃血清"

#. ~ Description for Strong stomach serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"fortitude of digestive systems."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增强消化系统的强韧度。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Good memory serum"
msgid_plural "Good memory serums"
msgstr[0] "好记性血清"

#. ~ Description for Good memory serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Improves "
"long and short term memory."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。改善长期和短期记忆力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Deftness serum"
msgid_plural "Deftness serums"
msgstr[0] "敏捷血清"

#. ~ Description for Deftness serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Improves "
"recovery from attacks that didn't connect with a target via an increased "
"fight response reflex."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。通过增强的战斗反应反射来提高未命中目标的攻击恢复速度。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Substance tolerance serum"
msgid_plural "Substance tolerance serums"
msgstr[0] "物质耐受血清"

#. ~ Description for Substance tolerance serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Improves "
"your body's filtration of intoxicants."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。改善你身体对麻醉物的过滤能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Gourmand serum"
msgid_plural "Gourmand serums"
msgstr[0] "美食家血清"

#. ~ Description for Gourmand serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"dopamine production in response to ingesting good-tasting foods and expands "
"digestive system to accomodate more volume."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。提高摄入美食时的多巴胺分泌，并扩张消化系统以容纳更大容量。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Addiction resistance serum"
msgid_plural "Addiction resistance serums"
msgstr[0] "成瘾抵抗血清"

#. ~ Description for Addiction resistance serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lowers the "
"brain's reliance on external dopamine sources, effectively increasing "
"resistance to addictions."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。降低大脑对外部多巴胺来源的依赖，有效提高对成瘾的抵抗力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Animal empathy serum"
msgid_plural "Animal empathy serums"
msgstr[0] "动物共情血清"

#. ~ Description for Animal empathy serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Inserts an "
"instinctual movement pattern that activates in the presence of animals into "
"your brain that makes animals less skittish or untrustworthy of you."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。向大脑植入一种在动物面前会被激活的本能行为模式，使动物对你不再那么警惕或不信任。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Animal kinship serum"
msgid_plural "Animal kinship serums"
msgstr[0] "动物亲和血清"

#. ~ Description for Animal kinship serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"certain parts of your brain to make you move in the presence of animals in "
"such a way that makes most animals leave you alone or be curious enough that "
"they act in a friendly manner to check you out."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。重写大脑某些部分，使你在动物面前的动作让大多数动物不打扰你，甚至产生足够好奇心以友好的方式接近你。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Terrifier serum"
msgid_plural "Terrifier serums"
msgstr[0] "恐吓者血清"

#. ~ Description for Terrifier serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Modifies "
"your pheromones and the way you carry yourself to instill fear into the "
"minds of creatures, making them more likely to flee or be intimidated."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。改变你的信息素和举止方式，向生物灌输恐惧，使它们更可能逃跑或被威吓。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Disease resistance serum"
msgid_plural "Disease resistance serums"
msgstr[0] "疾病抵抗血清"

#. ~ Description for Disease resistance serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Enhances "
"your immune system against diseases."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增强你的免疫系统对抗疾病的能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Adrenaline serum"
msgid_plural "Adrenaline serums"
msgstr[0] "肾上腺素血清"

#. ~ Description for Adrenaline serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"the response and size of adrenal glands."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增大肾上腺的反应和体积。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Less sleep serum"
msgid_plural "Less sleep serums"
msgstr[0] "少眠血清"

#. ~ Description for Less sleep serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lessens "
"your body's reliance on sleep."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。降低你身体对睡眠的依赖。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Self awareness serum"
msgid_plural "Self awareness serums"
msgstr[0] "自我感知血清"

#. ~ Description for Self awareness serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"your awareness on your body's state of being."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增强你对自己身体状态的感知。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Masochism serum"
msgid_plural "Masochism serums"
msgstr[0] "受虐倾向血清"

#. ~ Description for Masochism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"your brain to associate pain with pleasure."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。重写你的大脑，让它将痛苦与快感关联起来。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lighter steps serum"
msgid_plural "Lighter steps serums"
msgstr[0] "轻盈步伐血清"

#. ~ Description for Lighter steps serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Changes "
"your movement patterns to make less noise while walking and lessens the "
"chance of triggering traps."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。改变你的行动模式以减少行走噪音，并降低触发陷阱的几率。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Robust genetics serum"
msgid_plural "Robust genetics serums"
msgstr[0] "稳健基因血清"

#. ~ Description for Robust genetics serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Supplements your DNA with buffers against damage and degeneration."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用缓冲剂补充你的DNA，抵御损伤和退化。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Scout serum"
msgid_plural "Scout serums"
msgstr[0] "侦察兵血清"

#. ~ Description for Scout serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"your sight range and allows you to see distant things better."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增加你的视野范围，让你能更好地看到远处的事物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Cannibalism serum"
msgid_plural "Cannibalism serums"
msgstr[0] "食人倾向血清"

#. ~ Description for Cannibalism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Rewrites "
"some sections of your brain to cause you to both crave and get an increase "
"in dopamine production when eating your own kind."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。重写大脑的某些区域，使你在食用同类时既渴望又获得多巴胺分泌的增加。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Psychopathy serum"
msgid_plural "Psychopathy serums"
msgstr[0] "冷血倾向血清"

#. ~ Description for Psychopathy serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"your capacity to care about moralistic actions and morality in general."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。消除你对道德行为和一般道德观念的在意能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Killer drive serum"
msgid_plural "Killer drive serums"
msgstr[0] "杀戮驱动血清"

#. ~ Description for Killer drive serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Heightens "
"dopamine production when killing something and as a result of that makes you "
"crave it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在杀死什么东西时提高多巴胺分泌，从而让你对此产生渴望。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Weak scent serum"
msgid_plural "Weak scent serums"
msgstr[0] "弱气味血清"

#. ~ Description for Weak scent serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"most of your odour-producing sweat glands and general smelliness."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。移除大部分产生体味的汗腺和一般的异味。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Prettification serum"
msgid_plural "Prettification serums"
msgstr[0] "美化血清"

#. ~ Description for Prettification serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Like "
"beauty creams, except you inject this one, and it actually works. Makes you "
"more appealing to look at."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。就像美容霜，只不过这个是注射的，而且真的有效。让你看起来更吸引人。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Heavy sleeper serum"
msgid_plural "Heavy sleeper serums"
msgstr[0] "沉睡血清"

#. ~ Description for Heavy sleeper serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lowers "
"your environmental reactivity while asleep."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。降低你睡眠时对环境刺激的反应。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Albinism serum"
msgid_plural "Albinism serums"
msgstr[0] "白化血清"

#. ~ Description for Albinism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Removes "
"the pigmentation from your body and removes your body's capability to "
"produce pigmentation."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。移除你身体的色素沉着，并使身体失去产生色素的能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rough skin serum"
msgid_plural "Rough skin serums"
msgstr[0] "粗糙皮肤血清"

#. ~ Description for Rough skin serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives your "
"skin a rough texture."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的皮肤变得粗糙。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "High nightvision serum"
msgid_plural "High nightvision serums"
msgstr[0] "高级夜视血清"

#. ~ Description for High nightvision serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"the amount of light-sensitive cones in your eyes to enable very good "
"nightvision."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增加你眼中感光锥细胞的数量，获得非常好的夜视能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Full nightvision serum"
msgid_plural "Full nightvision serums"
msgstr[0] "完美夜视血清"

#. ~ Description for Full nightvision serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"an abundance of light-sensitive cones in your eyes, granting better "
"nightsight than most creatures have, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果身体支持，为你眼中提供丰富的感光锥细胞，赋予比大多数生物更好的夜视能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Cephalopod eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Cephalopod eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "头足类眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for Cephalopod eyes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Mutates "
"your eye structure into that of a cephalopod."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的眼睛结构变为头足类动物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fey eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Fey eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "精灵眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for Fey eyes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Replaces "
"the pigmentation of your eyes with self-modulating chromatophores that can "
"only shift into various shades of green."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用只能变换为各种绿色调的自我调节色素细胞替换你眼睛的色素沉着。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Feline eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Feline eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "猫眼血清"

#. ~ Description for Feline eyes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Mutates "
"your eyes into those of a cat. Nightvision not included."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的眼睛突变为猫眼。不含夜视功能。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Bird eyes serums"
msgid_plural "Bird eyes serumss"
msgstr[0] "鸟类眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for Bird eyes serums
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Structurally changes your eyes to be similar to that of avians, heightening "
"visual acuity and perception, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在结构上将你的眼睛变得类似鸟类，提高你的视觉敏锐度和感知力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Infrared vision serum"
msgid_plural "Infrared vision serums"
msgstr[0] "红外视觉血清"

#. ~ Description for Infrared vision serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Changes "
"your eyes to see the infrared wavelengths, allowing you to see warm-blooded "
"creatures in the dark, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。改变你的眼睛以看到红外波长，让你能在黑暗中看到温血生物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lizard eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Lizard eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "蜥蜴眼睛血清"

#. ~ Description for Lizard eyes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Structurally mutates your eyes to be like a reptile's. Reptilian infrared "
"not included."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在结构上将你的眼睛突变为爬行动物眼睛。不含爬虫类红外视觉。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lizard infrared serum"
msgid_plural "Lizard infrared serums"
msgstr[0] "蜥蜴红外血清"

#. ~ Description for Lizard infrared serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Grants "
"your eyes the ability to see into the infrared spectrum like various "
"reptiles, physical changes may apply."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。赋予你的眼睛如各种爬行动物般看到红外光谱的能力，可能伴随外观变化。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Very fast healer serum"
msgid_plural "Very fast healer serums"
msgstr[0] "极速愈合血清"

#. ~ Description for Very fast healer serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"cell division rate in response to structural damage, improving your healing "
"factor above normal."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。提高细胞对结构损伤的分裂速度，将你的愈合能力提升到正常水平之上。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Regeneration serum"
msgid_plural "Regeneration serums"
msgstr[0] "再生血清"

#. ~ Description for Regeneration serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Cell "
"division rate in response to structural damage is increased to nearly "
"unnatural levels, improving healing to a very high degree."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将细胞对结构损伤的分裂速度提升到近乎非自然的水平，极大程度地提高愈合能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Reptilian healing serum"
msgid_plural "Reptilian healing serums"
msgstr[0] "爬虫愈合血清"

#. ~ Description for Reptilian healing serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Grants "
"self-setting and automatic fast repair to both skeletal breakage and wounds "
"of the flesh, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。赋予骨骼断裂和肉体伤口自我复位和自动快速修复的能力，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Very little sleep serum"
msgid_plural "Very little sleep serums"
msgstr[0] "极少睡眠血清"

#. ~ Description for Very little sleep serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows "
"your brain to perform short bursts of functions similar to REM sleep while "
"awake, lengthening times you're awake and lowering the amount of time you "
"need to sleep, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的大脑进行类似阿尔法的短时功能爆发。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Tireless serum"
msgid_plural "Tireless serums"
msgstr[0] "不知疲倦血清"

#. ~ Description for Tireless serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Your brain "
"constantly performs similar functions to REM sleep all the time, effectively "
"removing the need to sleep, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的大脑持续进行类似快速眼动睡眠的功能，使你永远不需要睡眠。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fangs serum"
msgid_plural "Fangs serums"
msgstr[0] "獠牙血清"

#. ~ Description for Fangs serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"a set of fangs."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你一副獠牙。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Incisors serum"
msgid_plural "Incisors serums"
msgstr[0] "门齿血清"

#. ~ Description for Incisors serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Grows your "
"frontal teeth into rodent-like incisors, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的门牙变为啮齿类门齿，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Nictitating membrane serum"
msgid_plural "Nictitating membrane serums"
msgstr[0] "瞬膜血清"

#. ~ Description for Nictitating membrane serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Restores "
"the nictitating membrane that humans have lost, allowing you to see "
"underwater. Side effects may apply."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。恢复人类已退化的瞬膜，让你能在水下视物。可能伴随副作用。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Gills serum"
msgid_plural "Gills serums"
msgstr[0] "鳃血清"

#. ~ Description for Gills serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"gills, allowing you to breathe underwater."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你一副鳃，让你能水下呼吸。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Cephalopodic gills serum"
msgid_plural "Cephalopodic gills serums"
msgstr[0] "头足类鳃血清"

#. ~ Description for Cephalopodic gills serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"the gills of an octopus or squid, allowing you to breathe underwater."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你章鱼或鱿鱼般的鳃，让你能水下呼吸。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Scales serum"
msgid_plural "Scales serums"
msgstr[0] "鳞片血清"

#. ~ Description for Scales serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body with green reptilian scales."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用绿色爬虫鳞片覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Thick scales serum"
msgid_plural "Thick scales serums"
msgstr[0] "厚鳞血清"

#. ~ Description for Thick scales serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in thick, heavy green reptilian scales."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用厚实沉重的绿色爬虫鳞片覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Sleek scales serum"
msgid_plural "Sleek scales serums"
msgstr[0] "光滑鳞片血清"

#. ~ Description for Sleek scales serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in sleek, hydrodynamic scales like a fish."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用鱼一般光滑流线的鳞片覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Light bones serum"
msgid_plural "Light bones serums"
msgstr[0] "轻骨血清"

#. ~ Description for Light bones serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Lightens "
"your bones, making you faster but weaker."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。减轻你的骨骼，让你更快但更脆弱。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Feathers serum"
msgid_plural "Feathers serums"
msgstr[0] "羽毛血清"

#. ~ Description for Feathers serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in feathers."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用羽毛覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Down serum"
msgid_plural "Down serums"
msgstr[0] "绒羽血清"

#. ~ Description for Down serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"a fine layer of down feathers, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你一层细密的绒羽，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lightly furred serum"
msgid_plural "Lightly furred serums"
msgstr[0] "轻毛血清"

#. ~ Description for Lightly furred serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in a fine layer of fur."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用一层细密毛皮覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Furry serum"
msgid_plural "Furry serums"
msgstr[0] "毛皮血清"

#. ~ Description for Furry serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in a thick layer of fur."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用一层厚毛皮覆盖你的身体。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Shaggy fur serum"
msgid_plural "Shaggy fur serums"
msgstr[0] "蓬毛血清"

#. ~ Description for Shaggy fur serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Covers "
"your body in a very thick layer of fur like that of a bear."
