msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。用毛茸茸的几丁质甲壳覆盖你的表皮。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Urticating hairs serum"
msgid_plural "Urticating hairs serums"
