msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你精灵耳朵。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rodent ears serum"
msgid_plural "Rodent ears serums"
msgstr[0] "啮齿动物耳血清"

#. ~ Description for Rodent ears serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
