msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你啮齿动物的耳朵。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Web walker serum"
msgid_plural "Web walker serums"
msgstr[0] "蛛网行者血清"

#. ~ Description for Web walker serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to walk through webs without being slowed."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。允许你在蛛网中行走而不被减速。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Web weaver serum"
msgid_plural "Web weaver serums"
msgstr[0] "织网者血清"

#. ~ Description for Web weaver serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"the capabilities to produce your own webbing, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。赋予你产生蛛网的能力，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Web diver serum"
msgid_plural "Web diver serums"
msgstr[0] "蛛网垂降血清"

#. ~ Description for Web diver serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to use your webs as a way to scale shear drops, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。允许你利用蛛网攀爬陡峭悬崖，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rope webs serum"
msgid_plural "Rope webs serums"
msgstr[0] "蛛绳索血清"

#. ~ Description for Rope webs serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to make ropes from your spider silk, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。允许你用蛛丝制作绳索，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Arachnitect serum"
msgid_plural "Arachnitect serums"
msgstr[0] "蛛网建筑师血清"

#. ~ Description for Arachnitect serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to use webs to spin suspended walkways between ledges to span small gaps, if "
"your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。允许你用蛛网在岩架间编织悬空走道来跨越小间隙，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Whiskers serum"
msgid_plural "Whiskers serums"
msgstr[0] "胡须血清"

#. ~ Description for Whiskers serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"gives you feline whiskers."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你猫科动物的胡须。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Wiry whiskers serum"
msgid_plural "Wiry whiskers serums"
msgstr[0] "硬胡须血清"

#. ~ Description for Wiry whiskers serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"gives you rodent whiskers."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你啮齿动物的胡须。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fat deposits serum"
msgid_plural "Fat deposits serums"
msgstr[0] "脂肪沉积血清"

#. ~ Description for Fat deposits serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain "
"weight instantly! Fitness nuts hate this!"
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。立即增重！健身达人们恨死这个了！"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Enlargening serum"
msgid_plural "Enlargening serums"
msgstr[0] "增大血清"

#. ~ Description for Enlargening serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. Try this enlargement serum and get bigger, today! Large "
"Inc. is not responsible for any lack of growth due to unsupported "
"infratructure."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。试试这款增大血清，今天就变大吧！Large公司对因基础设施不足导致的增长缺乏不承担任何责任。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Enhugement serum"
msgid_plural "Enhugement serums"
msgstr[0] "巨大化血清"

#. ~ Description for Enhugement serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"HUUUGE!!! If your body can support it..."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得巨——大！！！如果你的身体能承受的话……"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extremely strong serum"
msgid_plural "Extremely strong serums"
msgstr[0] "极强力量血清"

#. ~ Description for Extremely strong serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Dude, "
"you're ripped!"
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。兄弟，你肌肉爆裂了！"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insanely strong serum"
msgid_plural "Insanely strong serums"
msgstr[0] "疯狂力量血清"

#. ~ Description for Insanely strong serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. Argh! Look at my bulging muscles!"
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。呃啊！看看我这隆起的肌肉！"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Alpha strength serum"
msgid_plural "Alpha strength serums"
msgstr[0] "阿尔法力量血清"

#. ~ Description for Alpha strength serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. It's only natural that an alpha such as I be this strong."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。像我这样的阿尔法强者有这般力量是理所当然的。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extremely dextrous serum"
msgid_plural "Extremely dextrous serums"
msgstr[0] "极强敏捷血清"

#. ~ Description for Extremely dextrous serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You can do "
"card tricks now."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你现在能表演纸牌戏法了。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insanely dextrous serum"
msgid_plural "Insanely dextrous serums"
msgstr[0] "疯狂敏捷血清"

#. ~ Description for Insanely dextrous serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You can do "
"that trick with the coin flipping between your knuckles, if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你能表演那个硬币在指关节间翻转的戏法了，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Alpha dexterity serum"
msgid_plural "Alpha dexterity serums"
msgstr[0] "阿尔法敏捷血清"

#. ~ Description for Alpha dexterity serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. Alphas ought to be this dextrous, yes."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。阿尔法应该如此灵巧，没错。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extremely intelligent serum"
msgid_plural "Extremely intelligent serums"
msgstr[0] "极强智力血清"

#. ~ Description for Extremely intelligent serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Deep blue "
"has no chance against you."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。深蓝不是你的对手。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insanely intelligent serum"
msgid_plural "Insanely intelligent serums"
msgstr[0] "疯狂智力血清"

#. ~ Description for Insanely intelligent serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. You've passed the singularity."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。你已经超越了奇点。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Alpha intelligence serum"
msgid_plural "Alpha intelligence serums"
msgstr[0] "阿尔法智力血清"

#. ~ Description for Alpha intelligence serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation, if your "
"body supports it. Non-alphas are such intellectual plebeians."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变，如果你的身体支持此种变化。非阿尔法的智力真是平民水平。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extremely perceptive serum"
msgid_plural "Extremely perceptive serums"
msgstr[0] "极强感知血清"

#. ~ Description for Extremely perceptive serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Perceive "
"most things."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。感知大多数事物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insanely perceptive serum"
msgid_plural "Insanely perceptive serums"
msgstr[0] "疯狂感知血清"

#. ~ Description for Insanely perceptive serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum, designed to give you a single mutation. Perceive "
"all there is around you, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。感知你周围的一切，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#. ~ Description for Alpha intelligence serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Alphas are "
"able to perceive the smallest of details, of course, if your body supports "
"it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。阿尔法当然能感知最微小的细节，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Distributed neurology serum"
msgid_plural "Distributed neurology serums"
msgstr[0] "分布式神经血清"

#. ~ Description for Distributed neurology serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. "
"Distributes your brain across your slimy body. Become basically one big "
"brain, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的大脑分布在黏液身体中。基本上变成一个巨大的大脑，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Distributed senses serum"
msgid_plural "Distributed senses serums"
msgstr[0] "分布式感官血清"

#. ~ Description for Distributed senses serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"capable of growing and retracting sensory organs at will, if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得能随意生长和收回感觉器官，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Tiny serum"
msgid_plural "Tiny serums"
msgstr[0] "微小血清"

#. ~ Description for Tiny serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"half your original size, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变为原来的一半大小，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Unassuming serum"
msgid_plural "Unassuming serums"
msgstr[0] "不起眼血清"

#. ~ Description for Unassuming serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Master the "
