msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。掌握微小的形态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Crafty serum"
msgid_plural "Crafty serums"
msgstr[0] "机敏血清"

#. ~ Description for Crafty serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become as "
"crafty as a mouse, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得像老鼠一样狡猾，如果你的身体支持的话。"

