msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得苍白的皮肤。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Spots serum"
msgid_plural "Spots serums"
msgstr[0] "斑点血清"

#. ~ Description for Spots serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Becomes "
"the collection of polkadots you've always wanted to be."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变成你一直想变成的波点图案。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Beautification serum"
msgid_plural "Beautification serums"
msgstr[0] "美化血清"

#. ~ Description for Beautification serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"beautiful."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得美丽。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Deluxe beautification serum"
msgid_plural "Deluxe beautification serums"
msgstr[0] "豪华美化血清"

#. ~ Description for Deluxe beautification serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"very beautiful."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得非常美丽。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Glorification serum"
msgid_plural "Glorification serums"
msgstr[0] "荣耀美化血清"

#. ~ Description for Glorification serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"glorious."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变得光辉耀眼。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Snout serum"
msgid_plural "Snout serums"
msgstr[0] "口鼻血清"

#. ~ Description for Snout serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Get a "
"snout."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得一个口鼻部。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Bovine snout serum"
msgid_plural "Bovine snout serums"
msgstr[0] "牛口鼻血清"

#. ~ Description for Bovine snout serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become the "
"source of cowlicks."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变成旋发的源头。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lupine muzzle serum"
msgid_plural "Lupine muzzle serums"
msgstr[0] "狼吻血清"

#. ~ Description for Lupine muzzle serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You were "
"always more of a dog person anyway."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。反正你一直更像是个爱狗人士。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Ursine muzzle serum"
msgid_plural "Ursine muzzle serums"
msgstr[0] "熊吻血清"

#. ~ Description for Ursine muzzle serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Maybe now "
"you can lick out those honeypots."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。也许现在你能舔到那些蜜罐里的蜜了。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rodent muzzle serum"
msgid_plural "Rodent muzzle serums"
msgstr[0] "啮齿吻血清"

#. ~ Description for Rodent muzzle serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Get a rat "
"face."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得一张老鼠脸。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Reptilian muzzle serum"
msgid_plural "Reptilian muzzle serums"
msgstr[0] "爬虫吻血清"

#. ~ Description for Reptilian muzzle serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Reptile "
"mouth ahoy."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。爬虫嘴巴来啦。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Proboscis serum"
msgid_plural "Proboscis serums"
msgstr[0] "口器血清"

#. ~ Description for Proboscis serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Whether "
"you're more like a fly or a mosquito after this is for you to figure out, if "
"your body supports it..."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。之后你更像苍蝇还是蚊子，由你自己决定，如果你的身体支持的话……"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Hollow bones serum"
msgid_plural "Hollow bones serums"
msgstr[0] "中空骨骼血清"

#. ~ Description for Hollow bones serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Hollows "
"out your bones like a bird's, making you faster but not capable of carrying "
"a lot."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。像鸟类一样掏空你的骨骼，让你更快但负重能力下降。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Vomitous serum"
msgid_plural "Vomitous serums"
msgstr[0] "呕吐血清"

#. ~ Description for Vomitous serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Why anyone "
"would want to throw up a lot is their business."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。为什么有人会想经常呕吐是他们的私事。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Persistence hunter serum"
msgid_plural "Persistence hunter serums"
msgstr[0] "持久猎手血清"

#. ~ Description for Persistence hunter serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to pursue prey for miles at a variety of paces until they stop from "
"exhaustion."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你能以各种步调追猎数英里，直到猎物因精疲力竭而停下。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extreme persistence hunter serum"
msgid_plural "Extreme persistence hunter serums"
msgstr[0] "极限持久猎手血清"

#. ~ Description for Extreme persistence hunter serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Allows you "
"to pursue prey for days until they literally die from exhaustion, if your "
"body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你能追猎数天，直到猎物真的因精疲力竭而死亡，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fast metabolism serum"
msgid_plural "Fast metabolism serums"
msgstr[0] "快速代谢血清"

#. ~ Description for Fast metabolism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increases "
"your metabolic rate and caloric burn."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。提高你的代谢率和热量消耗。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rapid metabolism serum"
msgid_plural "Rapid metabolism serums"
msgstr[0] "急速代谢血清"

#. ~ Description for Rapid metabolism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You'll "
"require more resources than most, but heal more rapidly."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你比大多数人需要更多资源，但愈合更快。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Very fast metabolism serum"
msgid_plural "Very fast metabolism serums"
msgstr[0] "极速代谢血清"

#. ~ Description for Very fast metabolism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You'll "
"need to eat a lot but your stamina regeneration isn't anything to sneeze at."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你需要大量进食，但你的耐力恢复速度不可小觑。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Extreme metabolism serum"
msgid_plural "Extreme metabolism serums"
msgstr[0] "极限代谢血清"

#. ~ Description for Extreme metabolism serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. How you "
"sustain yourself is anybody's guess but you've got a lot of endurance to "
"show for it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你怎么维持自己没人知道，但你因此获得了大量耐力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Metabolic rehydration serum"
msgid_plural "Metabolic rehydration serums"
msgstr[0] "代谢补水血清"

#. ~ Description for Metabolic rehydration serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain "
"moisture from what you eat and have your hunger and thirst be equal, like "
"mice, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。从食物中获取水分，使饥渴程度等同，像老鼠一样，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Very heavy sleeper serum"
msgid_plural "Very heavy sleeper serums"
msgstr[0] "极重睡眠血清"

#. ~ Description for Very heavy sleeper serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Sleep "
"through gunfire."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在枪炮声中也能酣睡。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Webbed extremities serum"
msgid_plural "Webbed extremities serums"
msgstr[0] "蹼肢血清"

#. ~ Description for Webbed extremities serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain "
"webbed hands and feet."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得蹼状的手和脚。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Paws serum"
msgid_plural "Paws serums"
msgstr[0] "掌血清"

#. ~ Description for Paws serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Turn your "
"hands into quasi-paws."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的手变为似掌状。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Broad paws serum"
msgid_plural "Broad paws serums"
msgstr[0] "宽掌血清"

#. ~ Description for Broad paws serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Turn your "
"hands into large paws that're better at swimming but manula dexteriry and "
"manipulation is going to be a problem."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的手变为适合游泳的大爪子，但手工灵巧和精细操作将成问题。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Beak serum"
msgid_plural "Beak serums"
msgstr[0] "喙血清"

#. ~ Description for Beak serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain the "
"beak of a bird that'll allow you to peck at things."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得鸟类的喙，让你能啄东西。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Woodpecker beak serum"
msgid_plural "Woodpecker beak serums"
msgstr[0] "啄木鸟喙血清"

#. ~ Description for Woodpecker beak serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain the "
"beak of a woodpecker and peck at enemies all day long, if your body supports "
"it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得啄木鸟的喙，整天啄敌人，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Hummingbird beak serum"
msgid_plural "Hummingbird beak serums"
msgstr[0] "蜂鸟喙血清"

#. ~ Description for Hummingbird beak serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain a "
"hummingbird beak, making those flowers look mighty tasty, if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得蜂鸟喙让花朵看起来美味无比，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Radioactivity serum"
msgid_plural "Radioactivity serums"
msgstr[0] "放射性血清"

#. ~ Description for Radioactivity serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"slightly radioactive for whatever reason."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。因某种原因变得略带放射性。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Slimy serum"
msgid_plural "Slimy serums"
msgstr[0] "黏液血清"

#. ~ Description for Slimy serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Be always "
"coated in a fine layer of slime."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。始终覆盖在一层细密的黏液中。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Viscous serum"
msgid_plural "Viscous serums"
msgstr[0] "黏稠血清"

#. ~ Description for Viscous serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Increase "
"your body's slime output to be sticky and gel-like, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。增加身体的黏液分泌，使其黏稠呈凝胶状，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Amorphous body serum"
msgid_plural "Amorphous body serums"
msgstr[0] "无定形体血清"

#. ~ Description for Amorphous body serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Make your "
"flesh and pleasing gel-like consistency, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。使你的肉质具有令人愉悦的凝胶状质地，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Omnicellular serum"
msgid_plural "Omnicellular serums"
msgstr[0] "全细胞血清"

#. ~ Description for Omnicellular serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become one "
"big cell, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。变成一个巨大的细胞，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Herbivore serum"
msgid_plural "Herbivore serums"
msgstr[0] "食草血清"

#. ~ Description for Herbivore serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become a "
"herbivore."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。成为草食动物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Carnivore serum"
msgid_plural "Carnivore serums"
msgstr[0] "食肉血清"

#. ~ Description for Carnivore serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become a "
"carnivore."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。成为肉食动物。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Vine limbs serum"
msgid_plural "Vine limbs serums"
msgstr[0] "藤蔓肢体血清"

#. ~ Description for Vine limbs serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain vine-"
"like limbs to lash at things with or rappel down drops."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得藤蔓般的肢体，可用于鞭打或下降。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Vine sprouter serum"
msgid_plural "Vine sprouter serums"
msgstr[0] "藤蔓发芽血清"

#. ~ Description for Vine sprouter serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain full "
"control over vine limbs and their detachment, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得对藤蔓肢体及其分离的完全控制，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Hair roots serum"
msgid_plural "Hair roots serums"
msgstr[0] "发根血清"

#. ~ Description for Hair roots serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Have roots "
"growing from out of your hair."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让根须从你的头发中长出。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Roots serum"
msgid_plural "Roots serums"
msgstr[0] "根须血清"

#. ~ Description for Roots serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain roots "
"for feet, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得根须作为脚，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rooter serum"
msgid_plural "Rooter serums"
msgstr[0] "扎根者血清"

#. ~ Description for Rooter serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"better at rooting yourself at the cost of being slower on diggable terrain, "
"if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。更擅长扎根自己，代价是在可挖掘地形上变慢，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Chloromorphosis serum"
msgid_plural "Chloromorphosis serums"
msgstr[0] "叶绿体变形血清"

#. ~ Description for Chloromorphosis serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Sleeping "
"on diggable soil will satisfy any hunger or thirst you might have, if your "
"body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在可挖掘土壤上睡觉将满足你的所有饥渴，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Mycorrhizal communion serum"
msgid_plural "Mycorrhizal communion serums"
msgstr[0] "菌根交感血清"

#. ~ Description for Mycorrhizal communion serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Talk to "
"trees like a sane being, if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。像一个正常存在一样与树木交谈，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Cold blooded serum"
msgid_plural "Cold blooded serums"
msgstr[0] "冷血血清"

#. ~ Description for Cold blooded serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You're "
"slower the colder it gets but you don't have to eat as much."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。越冷你越慢，但你不需要吃那么多。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Ectothermic serum"
msgid_plural "Ectothermic serums"
msgstr[0] "变温血清"

#. ~ Description for Ectothermic serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. You're "
"even slower the colder it gets but at least your food needs are even lower, "
"if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你越冷越慢，但至少食物需求也更低，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Growling serum"
msgid_plural "Growling serums"
msgstr[0] "低吼血清"

#. ~ Description for Growling serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain a "
"growl in your voice."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的声音带上低吼。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Snarling serum"
msgid_plural "Snarling serums"
msgstr[0] "咆哮血清"

#. ~ Description for Snarling serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain a "
"snarl in your voice."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的声音带上咆哮。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Hissing serum"
msgid_plural "Hissing serums"
msgstr[0] "嘶嘶血清"

#. ~ Description for Hissing serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain a "
"hiss in your voice."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的声音带上嘶嘶声。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Feathered arms serum"
msgid_plural "Feathered arms serums"
msgstr[0] "羽臂血清"

#. ~ Description for Feathered arms serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Get "
"feathers on your arms. Not much use beyond waterproofing and very minor "
"protection."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。在你的手臂上长出羽毛。除了防水和极轻微防护外没什么用。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Insect arms serum"
msgid_plural "Insect arms serums"
msgstr[0] "虫臂血清"

#. ~ Description for Insect arms serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Sprout two "
"extra insect-like arms. They don't have much use currently."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。长出两只额外的昆虫般手臂。目前没什么用。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Arachnid arms serum"
msgid_plural "Arachnid arms serums"
msgstr[0] "蛛臂血清"

#. ~ Description for Arachnid arms serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Sprout "
"four extra arachnidian arms. They don't have much use currently, if your "
"body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。长出四只额外的蛛形手臂。目前没什么用，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "8 tentacle arms serum"
msgid_plural "8 tentacle arms serums"
msgstr[0] "八触手臂血清"

#. ~ Description for 8 tentacle arms serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain 8 "
"tentacle arms."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得8条触手手臂。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Shell serum"
msgid_plural "Shell serums"
msgstr[0] "壳血清"

#. ~ Description for Shell serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain a "
"shell to protect you. Restricts and will destroy torso equipment on growth."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得保护你的壳。生长时会限制并摧毁躯干装备。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Roomy shell serum"
msgid_plural "Roomy shell serums"
msgstr[0] "宽敞壳血清"

#. ~ Description for Roomy shell serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Turn your "
"shell into one you can sleep in and gain warmth in."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的壳变为可以睡觉并在其中获得温暖的壳。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Tentacle legs serum"
msgid_plural "Tentacle legs serums"
msgstr[0] "触手腿血清"

#. ~ Description for Tentacle legs serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Swap your "
"legs for some tentacles."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的腿换为一些触手。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Tentacle bracing serum"
msgid_plural "Tentacle bracing serums"
msgstr[0] "触手支撑血清"

#. ~ Description for Tentacle bracing serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Give your "
"lower tentacles some suckers to keep you in place if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你的下部触手一些吸盘以固定你的位置，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Feline flexibility serum"
msgid_plural "Feline flexibility serums"
msgstr[0] "猫科柔韧血清"

#. ~ Description for Feline flexibility serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"changes your muscles, joints, and the movement center of your brain "
"internally somewhat, allowing you to traverse obstacles with ease, it also "
"helps you avoid attacks a bit more easily."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。这款血清从内部改变你的肌肉、关节和大脑运动中枢，让你轻松穿越障碍，还能略微帮助你躲避攻击。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Acidproof serum"
msgid_plural "Acidproof serums"
msgstr[0] "耐酸血清"

#. ~ Description for Acidproof serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Make your "
"flesh immune to acid if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。让你的血肉免疫酸蚀，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Acid blood serum"
msgid_plural "Acid blood serums"
msgstr[0] "酸血血清"

#. ~ Description for Acid blood serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Turn your "
"blood into acid, make them regret hurting you if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。将你的血液变为酸液，让他们后悔伤害你，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Amphibious serum"
msgid_plural "Amphibious serums"
msgstr[0] "两栖血清"

#. ~ Description for Amphibious serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"amphibiousm comfortable both on land and in water if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。成为两栖生物，在水陆都能舒适生活，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Lidless eyes serum"
msgid_plural "Lidless eyes serums"
msgstr[0] "无睑血清"

#. ~ Description for Lidless eyes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Remove "
"your eyelids and replace them with a see-through membrane if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。移除你的眼睑并以透明膜代替，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Aqueous repose serum"
msgid_plural "Aqueous repose serums"
msgstr[0] "水性休眠血清"

#. ~ Description for Aqueous repose serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Falling "
"asleep underwater should be easier now if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。现在在水下入睡应该更容易了，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Freshwater osmosis serum"
msgid_plural "Freshwater osmosis serums"
msgstr[0] "淡水渗透血清"

#. ~ Description for Freshwater osmosis serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Hydrate "
"your body by being in water if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。通过泡在水中为身体补水，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Electroreceptors serum"
msgid_plural "Electroreceptors serums"
msgstr[0] "电感受器血清"

#. ~ Description for Electroreceptors serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Become "
"capable of seeing robots and electric creatures through walls but be weak to "
"shocks."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。能够透过墙壁感知机器人和带电生物，但易受电击。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Toxic skin serum"
msgid_plural "Toxic skin serums"
msgstr[0] "毒皮血清"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Shark teeth serum"
msgid_plural "Shark teeth serums"
msgstr[0] "鲨齿血清"

#. ~ Description for Shark teeth serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain sharp "
"teeth like those of a shark and shed and replace them frequently if your "
"body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得鲨鱼般的尖牙，并能频繁脱落更换，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Fast reflexes serum"
msgid_plural "Fast reflexes serums"
msgstr[0] "快速反射血清"

#. ~ Description for Fast reflexes serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain "
"faster reflexes and improve your dodging."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得更快的反射神经，提高你的闪避能力。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit ears serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit ears serums"
msgstr[0] "兔耳血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit ears serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Your ears "
"become long and pointed, giving them exceptional hearing that picks up even "
"the faintest sounds around them."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的耳朵变得又长又尖，听力异常敏锐，能捕捉周围最微弱的声音。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit tail serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit tail serums"
msgstr[0] "兔尾血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit tail serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gives you "
"a cute, fluffy tail. It's cute, adorable, and beautiful."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。给你一条可爱蓬松的尾巴。可爱、迷人又美丽。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit fur serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit fur serums"
msgstr[0] "兔毛血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit fur serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Your "
"entire body is covered in soft, thick rabbit fur, which protects you from "
"the cold."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的全身覆盖着柔软厚实的兔毛，保护你免受寒冷。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit feet serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit feet serums"
msgstr[0] "兔足血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit feet serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Your feet "
"transform into the paws of a giant rabbit. You feel as though your kicks "
"have become more powerful and your luck has improved."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的脚变为巨兔的爪子。你感觉踢击变得更强有力，运气也变好了。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit nose serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit nose serums"
msgstr[0] "兔鼻血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit nose serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Your nose "
"turns into a twitching rabbit nose."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。你的鼻子变成一只抽动的兔子鼻。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Rabbit threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Rabbit threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "兔子阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Rabbit threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more rabbit-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像兔子的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Serpent threshold serum"
msgid_plural "Serpent threshold serums"
msgstr[0] "蛇类阈值血清"

#. ~ Description for Serpent threshold serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more serpent-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此种变化，它将永久使你的身体适应更像蛇类的状态。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Snake body serum"
msgid_plural "Snake body serums"
msgstr[0] "蛇身血清"

#. ~ Description for Snake body serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Two legs "
"fuse completely, transforming into the lower body of a giant snake."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。两条腿完全融合，变身为巨蛇的下半身。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Serpentine body serum"
msgid_plural "Serpentine body serums"
msgstr[0] "蛇形体血清"

#. ~ Description for Serpentine body serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. With the "
"lower body of a giant snake, you can glide effortlessly over any terrain., "
"if your body supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。拥有巨蛇的下半身，你能在任何地形上毫不费力地滑行，如果你的身体支持的话。"

#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid "Crushing coils serum"
msgid_plural "Crushing coils serums"
msgstr[0] "绞杀缠绕血清"

#. ~ Description for Crushing coils serum
#: .\mutations\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will make your tail as strong and powerful as an anaconda's. if your body "
"supports it."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。这款血清将让你的尾巴变得像蟒蛇一样强壮有力，如果你的身体支持的话。"




